amily 与 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：shared coarse 分支仍保持双 shared banks，但 routed cleanup 从固定 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 改为按 token 难度自适应启用 1 或 2 个 PK experts；与 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：shared coarse 容量从 1 个 shared bank 扩到 2 个。","exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu', k=32, expansion_factor=1, stage1_ratio=0.25, num_experts=1024, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56)` 可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'ARCHITECTURE', value:'dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu'}], fallback_architecture='dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu')` 返回 `[]`。","本地 exact 成本复核：selection_accesses=294912 (`0.0703125x`)、deployment_accesses=163840 (`0.0390625x`)、combined_accesses=458752 (`0.109375x`)；与 r274/r275 的 dual-shared fixed-AE scaffold 同档，因此这是一个干净的 matched architecture probe。","兼容性注册表已补充该 family，当前解析结果为 `direct_compatible`；更新后本地计数为直接兼容 14 个、扩展兼容 25 个、不兼容 3 个。","当前 dual-shared scaffold 已给出真实正向证据：r275 相对 r274 在同成本下把 exceed 从 `0.177462` 压到 `0.172059`，说明这条新 scaffold 仍值得一次 architecture-level upgrade，而不是继续做 split 邻域细扫。"],"reference_round":275,"self_review":"这轮符合当前阶段约束。最近两轮 r274-r275 都停留在同一 dual-shared family 内，且 objective 仍未接近 incumbent；按策略此时应优先换结构槽位，而不是继续补 `STAGE1_RATIO` 近邻点。选择 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 而不是继续在 dual-shared 上做 `0.125/0.375` 分裂点，是因为它直接测试当前高优先级方向“variable-active path by difficulty”，同时完全建立在已有 winning scaffold 的近同成本升级上。代码侧仅新增最小 family，并完成 whitelist、factory dispatch、override allowlist、compatibility registry 与 exact-string smoke；没有新增 tunable key，因此不需要改 `config_resolution`、`runner` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。主要风险是 adaptive active 在单-shared 版本上曾给过弱负信号；但 dual-shared scaffold 已把 coarse 主干抬强，当前最有价值的问题正是这是否能让 difficulty-aware cleanup 真正发挥作用。","summary":"已新增并接通 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。建议以 r275 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 做一轮 matched architecture probe，直接裁决“更厚 shared coarse 主干 + 按难度可变 1-or-2 PK cleanup path”能否在与 dual-shared fixed-AE 完全同成本的 `0.109375x` 档位继续显著压低 exceed。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"]}
