research/history/logs/agent_round_0301.stdout.log:2372:research/history/logs/agent_action_0293.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"扩展兼容新结构 probe：`shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual` 的最终重构为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk^*(r1(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r1(x))} α_{e,j} b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(r2(x))} γ_m c_m，其中 r1(x)=x-Σ α_i^sh b_i^sh，r2(x)=x-Σ α_i^sh b_i^sh-Σ α_{e,j} b_{e,j}。shared coarse、adaptive PK expert cleanup 与 residual cleanup 都落在静态向量库上，在线侧仍是 LUTurbo/Lottable 可导出的查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿流水线，因此兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设是：在 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的 cleanup scaffold 上加入 difficulty-aware adaptive-active expert path，能比固定 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 更强地降低 hard-token exceed，而 cost proxy 基本不变。","summary":"已实际新增并集成 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual`，只在 `sparsify/` 落盘修改 whitelist 与 runtime dispatch/class implementation。该 family 复用 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的 shared + PK + residual scaffold，仅把 expert cleanup 改成 adaptive-active 选择。按本地 smoke 与 cost 估计，在继承 r282 的 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 配置下 total_cost_ratio 仍约 `0.12x`，与 r288/r292 同量级；这使本轮成为一个纯粹检验“variable-active cleanup 是否能显著压低 exceed”的 matched-cost architecture probe。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这是一次有信息增量的新结构 probe，而不是继续扫已平台化的 split 邻域。风险在于 cost proxy 不会奖励 adaptive-active 的轻路径，所以若 exceed 改善不够，这条线可能仍输给 incumbent；但它正面回答了当前最高价值的问题：在保留 shared+PK+residual scaffold 的同时，difficulty-aware cleanup 是否值得继续。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["已落盘新增 family：`shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual`，并完成 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch/class 接线。","本地 exact-string smoke 已通过：`shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual` 在 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 下可实例化并 forward/backward。","本地 cost 估计：selection_ratio≈0.08，deployment_ratio≈0.04，total_cost_ratio≈0.12；与 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 同量级，适合作为 matched-cost exceed probe。","该 family 的结构语义是：shared coarse 吃主干，adaptive-active PK experts 按难度做 cleanup，最后 tiny residual head 做全局 tail cleanup；兼容性应视为扩展兼容。"],"next_hypotheses":["若本轮 exceed 明显低于 r288/r292 且 objective 接近或优于 incumbent，再以该 family 为 anchor 做一次最小 knee 校准，例如 `STAGE1_RATIO` 或 residual split。","若本轮 objective 仍无改善，则可将‘adaptive-active + residual cleanup’这条线一并降级，后续应转向真正不同的 coarse/shared 表达方式，而不是继续在 PK cleanup 语义上叠层。","若本轮出现 sanity 或 registration 异常，优先把它当新 family 集成问题处理，并用同一 exact architecture string 重做 smoke/dispatch 检查。"],"reference_round":282}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0301.stdout.log:2373:research/history/round_summaries/round_0300.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u8bbe\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(r1(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e^\u03c4(r1(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + \u03a3_{m\u2208S_res^\u03c4(r2(x))} \u03b3_m(x) c_m`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `r1(x)=x-\u03a3_i \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh`\uff0c`r2(x)=r1(x)-\u03a3_{e,j} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`\uff1b`{b_i^sh}` \u662f always-on shared coarse \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`{b_{e,j}}` \u662f product-key \u8def\u7531\u5230\u7684\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`{c_m}` \u662f tiny residual \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c\u800c\u6700\u540e\u4e00\u6bb5 residual \u7cfb\u6570 `\u03b3_m(x)` \u4f7f\u7528 JumpReLU-gated residual scorer\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u65f6\uff0c\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared \u67e5\u8868 -> PK expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 -> JumpReLU residual \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 -> \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`\u3001`product_key_expert_jumprelu`\u3001`dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u7b49\u517c\u5bb9 family \u4ecd\u53ef\u53c2\u4e0e\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9 family \u53ea\u80fd\u4f5c\u4e3a\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u540e\u7eed\u51b3\u7b56\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u5728\u8fde\u7eed\u4e24\u8f6e `NUM_EXPERTS` \u6269\u5bb9\u5df2\u663e\u793a 3072 \u6709\u9650\u6b63\u4fe1\u53f7\u30014096 \u660e\u663e\u56de\u64a4\u4e4b\u540e\uff0c\u5f53\u524d low-K \u4e3b\u74f6\u9888\u66f4\u50cf\u662f hard-token tail cleanup \u8bed\u4e49\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u6269 routed bank \u7c92\u5ea6\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u5e94\u5207\u6362\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 incumbent family \u4e0a\u505a\u8fd1\u90bb\u63d2\u503c\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r282 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`\uff0c\u5176\u4f59 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=2048`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`\u3001`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4fdd\u6301\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u201c\u5728 winning shared+PK scaffold \u4e0a\uff0c\u628a\u6700\u7ec8 tiny residual cleanup \u4ece plain residual \u8bed\u4e49\u6362\u6210 JumpReLU-gated tail cleanup\u201d\u80fd\u5426\u66f4\u6709\u6548\u538b\u4f4e `exceed_alpha_0.50`\u3002\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u81ea\u68c0\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 `selection_accesses=325696`\u3001`deployment_accesses=163840`\u3001`combined_accesses=489536`\u3001`exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3\u9884\u7b97\uff1b\u82e5\u8981\u51fb\u8d25\u5f53\u524d incumbent `objective=0.2684179902076721`\uff0c\u9700\u8981\u628a `exceed_alpha_0.50` \u538b\u5230 `0.1517035126686096` \u4ee5\u4e0b\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0301.stdout.log:2376:research/history/logs/agent_action_0276.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{s=1..2} Σ_{i∈S_s^{k1}(x)} α_{s,i}^{sh}(x) b_{s,i}^{sh} + Σ_{e∈E_pk^*(r_sh(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^{τ,k2}(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j}(r_sh(x)) b_{e,j}，其中 {B_s^sh} 是两个 always-on shared 静态子库，r_sh(x)=x-Σ_sΣ_i α_{s,i}^{sh}(x)b_{s,i}^{sh}，E_pk^*(·) 表示在 residual 上由 product-key router 按 token 难度自适应启用 1 或 2 个静态 expert 子库，JumpReLU 只改变 expert 内局部 support。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared coarse 子库查表 + residual 上的 PK 路由 + 少量 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，不依赖动态字典，因此该 family 判定为直接兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：相对 r275 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 切到新 family `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，保持 `K=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=1024`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余 recipe 不变，在 exact 同成本 `total_cost_ratio=0.109375` 下引入 difficulty-aware variable-active cleanup path，能比固定 AE=2 的 dual-shared scaffold 更有效地处理 hard tokens，把 exceed_alpha_0.50 继续从 r275 的 `0.172059` 往下压，并争取逼近或击败 incumbent r266。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该 family 在同成本下明显优于 r275，并接近或击败 r266，则下一轮只改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.125`，测试在 adaptive cleanup 存在时是否重新回到更轻 coarse split 更优。","如果该 family 只比 r275 小幅更好但仍明显不够接近 incumbent，则记录为“variable-active path 有帮助，但不足以带来 regime shift”，后续应停止在 adaptive 邻域细扫。","如果该 family 不如 r275，则说明在当前 PK/shared scaffold 上 adaptive 1-or-2 expert path 不是主要突破口，后续应转向其他真正改变 cleanup 语义或 coarse 表达方式的新结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，真实改动文件为 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`、`research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md`。","该 family 与 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：shared coarse 分支仍保持双 shared banks，但 routed cleanup 从固定 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 改为按 token 难度自适应启用 1 或 2 个 PK experts；与 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：shared coarse 容量从 1 个 shared bank 扩到 2 个。","exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu', k=32, expansion_factor=1, stage1_ratio=0.25, num_experts=1024, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56)` 可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'ARCHITECTURE', value:'dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu'}], fallback_architecture='dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu')` 返回 `[]`。","本地 exact 成本复核：selection_accesses=294912 (`0.0703125x`)、deployment_accesses=163840 (`0.0390625x`)、combined_accesses=458752 (`0.109375x`)；与 r274/r275 的 dual-shared fixed-AE scaffold 同档，因此这是一个干净的 matched architecture probe。","兼容性注册表已补充该 family，当前解析结果为 `direct_compatible`；更新后本地计数为直接兼容 14 个、扩展兼容 25 个、不兼容 3 个。","当前 dual-shared scaffold 已给出真实正向证据：r275 相对 r274 在同成本下把 exceed 从 `0.177462` 压到 `0.172059`，说明这条新 scaffold 仍值得一次 architecture-level upgrade，而不是继续做 split 邻域细扫。"],"reference_round":275,"self_review":"这轮符合当前阶段约束。最近两轮 r274-r275 都停留在同一 dual-shared family 内，且 objective 仍未接近 incumbent；按策略此时应优先换结构槽位，而不是继续补 `STAGE1_RATIO` 近邻点。选择 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 而不是继续在 dual-shared 上做 `0.125/0.375` 分裂点，是因为它直接测试当前高优先级方向“variable-active path by difficulty”，同时完全建立在已有 winning scaffold 的近同成本升级上。代码侧仅新增最小 family，并完成 whitelist、factory dispatch、override allowlist、compatibility registry 与 exact-string smoke；没有新增 tunable key，因此不需要改 `config_resolution`、`runner` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。主要风险是 adaptive active 在单-shared 版本上曾给过弱负信号；但 dual-shared scaffold 已把 coarse 主干抬强，当前最有价值的问题正是这是否能让 difficulty-aware cleanup 真正发挥作用。","summary":"已新增并接通 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。建议以 r275 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 做一轮 matched architecture probe，直接裁决“更厚 shared coarse 主干 + 按难度可变 1-or-2 PK cleanup path”能否在与 dual-shared fixed-AE 完全同成本的 `0.109375x` 档位继续显著压低 exceed。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0301.stdout.log:2412:research/history/logs/agent_action_0300.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r1(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r1(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res^τ(r2(x))} γ_m(x) c_m`，其中 `r1(x)=x-Σ_i α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh`，`r2(x)=r1(x)-Σ_{e,j} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`；`{b_i^sh}` 是 always-on shared coarse 静态子库，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 product-key 路由到的静态 expert 子库，`{c_m}` 是 tiny residual 静态子库，而最后一段 residual 系数 `γ_m(x)` 使用 JumpReLU-gated residual scorer。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时，在线链路仍是“shared 查表 -> PK expert 子库查表 -> JumpReLU residual 子库查表 -> 有限加权和 -> 选择性在线补偿”，不涉及动态字典生成，因此该 family 判定为 `扩展兼容`。`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`、`product_key_expert_jumprelu`、`dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 等兼容 family 仍可参与当前 objective leaderboard；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 只能作为历史参考，不能驱动后续决策。本轮唯一主假设是：在连续两轮 `NUM_EXPERTS` 扩容已显示 3072 有限正信号、4096 明显回撤之后，当前 low-K 主瓶颈更像是 hard-token tail cleanup 语义，而不是继续扩 routed bank 粒度；因此应切换结构槽位，而不是继续在 incumbent family 上做近邻插值。相对 r282 只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`，其余 `K=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=2048`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 保持不变，直接测试“在 winning shared+PK scaffold 上，把最终 tiny residual cleanup 从 plain residual 语义换成 JumpReLU-gated tail cleanup”能否更有效压低 `exceed_alpha_0.50`。本地精确成本自检显示该点 `selection_accesses=325696`、`deployment_accesses=163840`、`combined_accesses=489536`、`exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`，满足预算；若要击败当前 incumbent `objective=0.2684179902076721`，需要把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到 `0.1517035126686096` 以下。","summary":"建议以 r282 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`。这轮不是继续做 incumbent 邻域扫参，而是在当前最强 shared+PK scaffold 上做一次 matched cleanup-semantics probe，直接判断 JumpReLU tail residual 能否在约 `0.1167x` 成本下把 exceed 明显压低。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮严格满足单变量原则：相对 r282 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。它也符合当前 round 300 的策略要求：最近两轮已经是同一 family 上的局部延伸且没有实质击穿 incumbent，因此本轮应优先换结构槽位，而不是继续做 `NUM_EXPERTS/K/STAGE1_RATIO` 近邻细扫。之所以选择这个 family，而不是再新开一个未注册 family，是因为它已经真实落盘、已完成 whitelist/factory/allowlist/smoke/cost 检查，并且当前本地 policy 校验已通过；r297 的失败只是当时全局 incubation 满额，而不是此 family 自身不可运行。主要风险是 JumpReLU 过度抑制 tiny residual bank，导致 tail cleanup 容量下降，结果不如 r292 的 plain residual；但这正是本轮要用一个最小结构切换清晰回答的问题。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual` 已在更早轮次真实落盘并完成注册，实际修改文件是 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`；本轮无需再做代码编辑。","该 family 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是静态 shared 子库 + 静态 PK expert 子库 + 静态 residual 子库上的有限加权和，兼容性标签应记为 `扩展兼容`。","本地 exact-string smoke、override allowlist 和成本自检都已通过；当前 recipe 下 `exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`。","r297 被 `policy_reject` 的原因仅是当时新 family 进入 incubating 时撞上 incubation 上限，不是 wiring 或兼容性错误；当前用本地 `validate_action(...)` 对同一 `ARCHITECTURE` param_only 提案复核已通过。","r298 与 r299 共同说明 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 上继续扩 `NUM_EXPERTS` 已接近 knee：3072 有限正信号，但 4096 已明显回撤，因此当前更该测试 cleanup 语义升级。","若本轮结果仍不能优于 r292 的 same-cost plain residual 版本，则 shared+PK 后接 tiny residual cleanup 这整条邻域应整体降级，不再继续细扫 residual 语义。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 `0.1167x` 成本下明显优于 r292，并接近或击败 incumbent，则下一轮留在该 family，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，校准 shared coarse 与 JumpReLU tail cleanup 的预算分工。","如果该点优于 r292 但仍未赢 incumbent，则说明 cleanup 语义升级方向成立但交换率仍不足；下一轮优先只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 向左探一格，尝试回收部分 cost 而保留 exceed 收益。","如果该点与 r292 持平或更差，则说明当前瓶颈不在 residual gating 语义；后续应停止沿 shared+PK+tiny-residual 邻域继续细扫，转向别的 scaffold-level cleanup 或 coarse 表达升级。"],"reference_round":282}
