research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:1382:research/history/round_summaries/round_0271.json:36:      "`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u7684 split \u8f74\u5df2\u57fa\u672c\u6536\u655b\uff1ar266 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` \u4f18\u4e8e r268 `0.5` \u4e0e r269 `0.125`\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u540e\u7eed\u4e0d\u5e94\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u8be5\u8f74\u4e0a\u6d88\u8017\u9884\u7b97\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:1392:research/history/logs/agent_action_0299.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"NUM_EXPERTS","value":"4096"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r_sh(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`，其中 `{b_i^sh}` 是 always-on shared coarse 静态子库，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 product-key 路由到的静态 expert 子库；在线导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared 查表 -> residual -> PK 选择少量静态 expert 子库 -> expert 内 JumpReLU sparse support -> 查表加权和 -> 选择性补偿”的静态子库有限加权和链路，因此该 family 判定为 `直接兼容`，不兼容 family 继续不得驱动当前 objective leaderboard。r298 已给出一个值得最小 follow-up 的新信号：相对 r282 只把 `NUM_EXPERTS 2048 -> 3072`，`exceed_alpha_0.50` 从 `0.168418` 降到 `0.162632`，而 exact total_cost 只从 `0.102295x` 升到 `0.107178x`，objective 仅差 incumbent 约 `0.001392`。因此本轮最有信息量的动作不是回到低信息的 `K/STAGE1_RATIO/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 近邻细扫，也不是在 incubation limit 仍阻塞的情况下继续新开 family，而是对同一高优先级“更细粒度 routed micro-experts”假设做一个必要的 knee 校准。相对 r298 本轮只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=4096`，其余 `K=32, EF=1, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, OPTIMIZER=adam, LR=8e-4` 保持不变，直接回答 finer-grained expert partitioning 是否还在继续换回足够的 hard-token exceed 改善。该配置本地精确成本复核为 `selection_accesses=303104`、`deployment_accesses=163840`、`combined_accesses=466944`、`exact total_cost_ratio=0.111328125`，仍稳定位于当前 `0.08~0.14` 主战场并满足预算；若要击败 incumbent `objective=0.2684179902076721`，需要把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到 `0.1570898652076721` 以下。相对 r298，这只要求再多拿回约 `0.00554` 的 exceed，而成本仅再增加 `0.00415x`，属于当前最值得验证的一次同轴 follow-up。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点击败 incumbent，则把结论记录为“更细粒度 micro-experts 在当前 shared+PK scaffold 上仍有正交换率”；下一轮不应继续无限制线性扩 bank，而应优先等待 incubation 槽位释放后，把这个更强 scaffold 与新的 cleanup 语义结合。","如果该点 exceed 继续下降但 objective 仍未赢过 incumbent，则可把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 轴视为已接近 knee：更细粒度 experts 有帮助，但不足以形成 regime shift；后续预算应转回新的 cleanup/coarse 结构槽位，而不是继续做 4096 以上的 bank 扩张。","如果该点与 r298 持平或更差，则可更明确地下调“继续扩 routed bank 粒度”这条线的优先级，认定当前主瓶颈不再是 expert partition granularity，而应是更强的 tail cleanup 机制。"],"notes_to_memory":["r298 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu @ NUM_EXPERTS=3072` 的真实结果为 objective=0.269810、cost=0.107178x、exceed=0.162632、fvu=0.14650991559028625；它没有赢 incumbent，但给出了更细粒度 micro-experts 可显著压低 exceed 的正信号。","本轮选择 `NUM_EXPERTS=4096` 是对同一高价值结构问题做一次最小 knee 校准，而不是回到 `K/STAGE1_RATIO/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 的低信息近邻扫点。","本地 smoke 已通过：`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 在 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=4096, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 下可 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 override allowlist 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'NUM_EXPERTS', value:'4096'}], fallback_architecture='shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu') == []`。","本地精确成本复核：`selection_accesses=303104`、`deployment_accesses=163840`、`combined_accesses=466944`、`exact total_cost_ratio=0.111328125`；低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","该点若想赢过 incumbent，需要 `exceed_alpha_0.50 <= 0.1570898652076721`；这是对 r298 当前 `0.162632` 再向下约 `0.00554` 的要求。"],"reference_round":298,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守单变量原则：相对 r298 只改 `NUM_EXPERTS`。之所以允许在同一 family 上再做一次 follow-up，是因为 r298 刚给出一个接近击败 incumbent 的新正信号，且这条轴直接对应当前 prompt 最高优先级之一“更细粒度 routed micro-experts”；这不是沿着旧的 `K/STAGE1_RATIO/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 平台继续机械细扫。主要风险是 3072->4096 可能已经进入收益递减区间，只会抬高 cost 而不给足够的 exceed 回报；但这正是本轮要用一个最小单变量实验回答的问题。","summary":"建议本轮以 r298 为 reference，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=4096`。这是对 r298 新正信号的一次必要 knee 校准，用来判断更细粒度 micro-experts 是否足以把 shared+PK scaffold 真正推过当前 incumbent，而不是继续把预算花在低信息近邻扫点上。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:1393:research/history/logs/agent_action_0272.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式写为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh^{k1}(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_var-pk(r1(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^{k2}(r1(x))} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 r1(x)=x-Σ α_i^sh(x)b_i^sh，第一项是 always-on shared coarse 静态库的有限加权和，第二项是在 residual 上由 product-key 路由选出的少量静态 expert 子库内做 JumpReLU 稀疏加权和，但 active expert 集合不再固定为 2，而是按 router 置信度对简单 token 只保留 1 expert、困难 token 仍保留 2 experts。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“shared 查表 -> residual -> PK 路由到静态 expert 子库 -> expert 内 sparse support -> 查表加权和 -> 选择性补偿”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此新 family `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 判定为直接兼容；不兼容 family `batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk`、`lowrank_adaptive_budget_residual` 继续只作历史参考，不参与当前兼容 leaderboard。r266 给出当前唯一 recent 正信号 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，而 r265 的 `adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 负信号只说明“没有 shared coarse 主干时，variable-active PK 不够”，并不能裁掉“shared+PK + variable-active path”这个更贴近 prompt 的结构槽位。最近两轮 r270/r271 没有把 objective 拉低，按规则应优先切换到新的结构槽位；当前最高信息量的新槽位正是把 recent 最强信号 `shared+PK` 与高优先级未决方向 `variable-active path by difficulty` 合并。该新 family 已实际落盘并完成 exact-string smoke；本地 exact 成本复核显示在当前 many-tiny recipe `K=32, NUM_EXPERTS=1024, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 下，combined_accesses=401408，exact total_cost_ratio=0.095703125，与 r266 完全同成本。因此相对 r266 只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 是当前最干净、信息增量最高的新结构 probe；要击败 r266 exact objective=0.275001125，只需 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.179298`。","summary":"已新增并本地验证 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。建议以 r266 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，做一轮新的 matched architecture probe，直接回答“shared coarse + PK cleanup + variable-active path by difficulty”是否能在同成本下压低 exceed。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮满足当前 round-272 的默认规则：最近两轮没有把 objective 明显拉低，因此优先切换到新的结构槽位，而不是继续沿 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 做 `K/LATENTS/STAGE1_RATIO` 细扫。之所以选这个新 family，而不是再回到 hash、PK-factorized、shared-lowrank 或旧的 adaptive-active non-shared 方向，是因为它直接承接当前唯一 recent 正信号 `shared+PK`，同时把变化局限在 prompt 明确高优先级、但尚未在这条主线上被验证过的“按难度自适应 active path”这一条结构轴上。工程改动被限制在必要文件：`sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`；没有新增 tunable env key，只是为新 architecture 接通现有 expert/STAGE1/JUMPRELU 参数集。主要风险是当前 cost proxy 仍按 worst-case `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 计费，因此这轮若成功只能体现为 exceed 改善而非 cost 下降；但这恰好让结构判断更干净。如果连这个“shared+PK 的更强 Expert-Choice 变体”都无法在 same-cost lane 改善 objective，就可以更有把握地下调 variable-active 方向在当前 hookpoint 上的优先级。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，改动位于 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`。","该 family 的精确语义是：`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的 always-on shared coarse stage，加上 `adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的 confidence-based 1-or-2 expert residual stage；不是旧 family 的重命名。","exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu', k=32, expansion_factor=1, num_experts=1024, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56, stage1_ratio=0.25, factorized_hidden_dim=256, trunk_rank=16)` 可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key: ARCHITECTURE, value: shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu}], fallback_architecture='shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu')` 返回空列表。","本地 exact 成本复核：`shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu K=32 NUM_EXPERTS=1024 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 的 selection_accesses=237568、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=401408、exact total_cost_ratio=0.095703125，与 r266 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 同成本。","r270 强烈否定了当前 hookpoint 上的 tiny factorized experts；r271 也说明沿 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 提高 K 到 48 虽能降 exceed 到 0.165215，但不足以覆盖额外 deployment 成本，因此这条 family 的简单 K 轴不应继续主导预算。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 在同 exact cost 下把 exceed 压到 0.179298 以下并优于 r266，则说明当前 best recent signal 不只是 shared+PK 分工本身，而是 shared coarse 主干与 variable-active cleanup 的组合；下一轮应留在该 family，只做一次容量或 split 的最小 follow-up。","如果该新 family 与 r266 基本持平或更差，则说明在当前 cost proxy 下，variable-active path by difficulty 并没有给 shared+PK 主线带来足够的 tail-error 改善；后续应停止沿这一方向继续加预算，转回其他新结构槽位。","如果该 family 只在曲线前中段更稳、但最终 objective 仍不如 r266，则说明它主要改善了 optimization 形状而非最终 exceed；那时更合理的下一问会是新的 router/coarse 机制，而不是继续在 variable-active 线上插值。"],"reference_round":266}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:1395:research/history/round_summaries/round_0282.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(r_sh(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e^\u03c4(r_sh(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `{b_i^sh}` \u662f always-on shared coarse \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`{b_{e,j}}` \u662f product-key \u8def\u7531\u5230\u7684\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff0c\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared \u67e5\u8868 -> residual -> PK \u9009\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> expert \u5185 JumpReLU sparse support -> \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r266 \u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u6539 `NUM_EXPERTS=2048`\uff0c\u5176\u4f59 `K=32, EF=1, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` \u4fdd\u6301\u4e0d\u53d8\uff1b\u8fd9\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u626b `K/STAGE1_RATIO/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` \u7684\u4f4e\u4fe1\u606f\u90bb\u57df\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5 DeepSeekMoE \u98ce\u683c\u7684\u201c\u66f4\u7ec6\u7c92\u5ea6 routed micro-experts\u201d\u80fd\u5426\u5728\u76f8\u540c\u77ed active path\u3001\u76f8\u540c deployment K \u4e0b\uff0c\u7528\u66f4\u5927\u7684\u9759\u6001 routed \u5bb9\u91cf\u628a hard-token exceed \u538b\u4f4e\u3002\u5f53\u524d scaffold \u7684\u6700\u65b0\u7ed3\u6784\u5347\u7ea7 r281 \u5df2\u8bf4\u660e\u201c\u66f4\u6df1\u7684\u540c expert-set cleanup\u201d\u4e0d\u591f\uff1b\u4e0b\u4e00\u6b65\u66f4\u6709\u4ef7\u503c\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u662f expert \u5206\u7247\u7c92\u5ea6\u672c\u8eab\u662f\u5426\u624d\u662f\u74f6\u9888\u3002\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\uff1a`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu K=32 NUM_EXPERTS=2048 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` \u7684 `selection_accesses=265216`\u3001`deployment_accesses=163840`\u3001`combined_accesses=429056`\u3001`exact total_cost_ratio=0.102294921875`\uff0c\u4ecd\u7a33\u5b9a\u4f4d\u4e8e\u5f53\u524d `0.08~0.14` \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u5185\u3002\u8981\u6253\u8d62 r266 \u7684 exact objective\u22480.275001\uff0c\u53ea\u9700\u628a `exceed_alpha_0.50` \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 `0.172706` \u4ee5\u4e0b\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:1408:research/history/round_summaries/round_0284.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u8bbe\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{s=1..2} \u03a3_{i\u2208S_s(x)} \u03b1_{s,i}^sh(x) b_{s,i}^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(r_sh(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e^\u03c4(r_sh(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d\u4e24\u4e2a always-on shared coarse \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93 `{b_{s,i}^sh}` \u5148\u5438\u6536\u66f4\u539a\u7684\u516c\u5171\u4e3b\u5e72\uff0c`{b_{e,j}}` \u662f product-key \u8def\u7531\u5230\u7684\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff0c\u5728\u7ebf\u63a8\u7406\u4ecd\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u591a shared \u67e5\u8868 + PK \u9009\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 + expert \u5185 JumpReLU sparse support + \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u6d41\u6c34\u7ebf\uff0c\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r282\uff0c\u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE=dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` \u4e0e\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u5728\u5df2\u7ecf\u88ab r282 \u8bc1\u660e\u6709\u6548\u7684 finer-grained micro-expert scaffold \u4e0a\uff0c\u66f4\u539a\u7684 shared coarse \u4e3b\u5e72\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5728\u8fd1\u540c\u6210\u672c\u4e0b\u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u538b\u4f4e hard-token exceed\u3002\u5b83\u4e0e\u5df2\u5931\u8d25\u7684 r283 adaptive-active probe \u4e0d\u540c\uff0c\u53d8\u5316\u4e0d\u5728 active-path\uff0c\u800c\u5728 coarse/shared \u8868\u8fbe\u80fd\u529b\uff1b\u8fd9\u6b63\u5bf9\u5e94\u5f53\u524d prompt \u66f4\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u7684\u201c\u5efa\u7acb\u5728 winning scaffold \u4e0a\u7684 shared/coarse \u8868\u8fbe\u5347\u7ea7\u201d\u3002\u672c\u5730\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\