research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:1447:research/history/logs/agent_action_0295.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"扩展兼容新结构 probe：`residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的最终重构为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i^{sh,1} b_i^{sh,1} + Σ_{j∈S_2(r1(x))} α_j^{sh,2} b_j^{sh,2} + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r2(x))} Σ_{m∈S_e^τ(r2(x))} α_{e,m} b_{e,m} + Σ_{u∈S_res(r3(x))} γ_u c_u，其中 r1/r2/r3 是逐级 residual。两层 shared residual coarse stage、PK-routed expert cleanup 与最后的 tiny global residual cleanup 都只访问静态向量库并做有限加权和，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿流水线，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设是：在 r294 已显出较好 exceed 的 dual-shared PK scaffold 上再加一个很小的全局 residual tail-cleanup，能比现有 dual-shared PK 更强地压住 hard-token exceed。","summary":"已实际新增并集成 `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual`，只修改 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。该 family 是对 r294 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的结构升级：保留双 shared coarse + PK cleanup，只再追加一个 tiny factorized residual cleanup。按本地 exact-string smoke 与 cost 估计，在继承 r294 的 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.375, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 配置下 total_cost_ratio 约 `0.13x`，仍在当前目标带内；因此本轮是一次 matched-cost 附近、明确面向降低 exceed 的 scaffold-upgrade probe。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"风险很直接：`cost≈0.13x` 已经要求 exceed 至少接近 `0.09~0.10` 才有机会逼近阶段目标，交换率门槛很高。如果这轮 exceed 只是比 r294 小幅下降几个点，仍不够支撑主线；但它是当前最贴近 winning scaffold 的高信息增量升级之一，值得用一轮回答。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["已落盘新增 family：`residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual`，完成了 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch/class 接线。","本地 exact-string smoke 已通过：`residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual` 在 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.375, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 下可实例化并 forward/backward。","本地 cost 估计：selection_ratio≈0.09，deployment_ratio≈0.04，total_cost_ratio≈0.13；处于当前允许的 matched-objective 探索带。","该 family 的结构语义是：dual shared residual coarse stage 吃主干，PK experts 做中层 cleanup，tiny factorized residual head 做尾部 cleanup；与 r294 相比，信息增量集中在 hard-token tail-cleanup 机制。"],"next_hypotheses":["若本轮 exceed 明显低于 r294 且 objective 改善，再以该 family 为 anchor 做一次极小幅 knee 校准，例如 `STAGE1_RATIO`。","若本轮 objective 仍无改善，则说明在 dual-shared PK scaffold 上追加 tiny global residual cleanup 的交换率不足，后续应停止继续叠加同类 cleanup 层。","若本轮出现 sanity 或 registration 异常，优先按 exact architecture string 回查 config whitelist / dispatch / class reachable 性，而不要把问题误判成训练质量结论。"],"reference_round":294}
