research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:1657:research/history/logs/agent_round_0287.stdout.log:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i^{sh,1}(x) b_i^{sh,1} + Σ_{j∈S_2(r_1(x))} α_j^{sh,2}(x) b_j^{sh,2} + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r_2(x))} Σ_{m∈S_e^τ(r_2(x))} γ_{e,m}(x) c_{e,m}`，其中 `r_1(x)=x-Σ_i α_i^{sh,1} b_i^{sh,1}`，`r_2(x)=r_1(x)-Σ_j α_j^{sh,2} b_j^{sh,2}`。两级 shared bank 与 PK-routed expert 子库都仍是静态子库；在线链路只是“shared bank 1 查表 -> residual -> shared bank 2 查表 -> residual -> product-key 选少量静态 expert 子库 -> expert 内 JumpReLU sparse support -> 查表加权和”，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态子库有限加权和推理链路，因此 `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 判定为直接兼容。明确不兼容 family 仍只作历史参考，不能驱动当前兼容 leaderboard。本轮唯一主假设是：r286 已经用 `product_key_expert_jumprelu@2048` 证明“仅靠更细 PK micro-experts 而去掉 shared coarse”不能赢过 incumbent；因此当前更高信息量的问题不是继续做 plain PK 或 shared-lowrank 的邻域微调，而是在保留 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 这条 winning scaffold 的前提下，测试一种真正不同的 cleanup 语义。相对 r282 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 切到 `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，保持 `NUM_EXPERTS=2048, K=32, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, EXPANSION_FACTOR=1, OPTIMIZER=adam, LR=8e-4` 与其余 recipe 不变，直接回答“把第二个 shared 分支改成 residual-only cleanup，而不是并行同层 coarse 竞争，是否能在近同成本下更强地压低 low-K tail exceed”。该 family 在 1024-expert 上只做过一次早期 probe，尚未在当前 2048 many-tiny scaffold 上做过 clean matched test，因此这不是旧线回潮，而是建立在当前 best scaffold 上的结构升级 probe。","summary":"以 r282 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，在同一 2048 many-tiny scaffold 上执行一轮 matched architecture probe，直接测试“串联 residual shared cleanup + PK routed cleanup”能否比当前 incumbent 更慢地恶化 hard-token exceed。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮严格满足单变量原则：相对 r282 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。之所以不继续围绕 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 做 `K/STAGE1_RATIO/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 近邻细扫，是因为最近 4 轮都未扩展 objective，且 prompt 明确要求此时优先换结构槽位。之所以不再回到 plain PK、shared-lowrank、stacked PK、factorized expert 或更老的 routed/shared-routed 线，是因为它们已经在当前 target 给出更强或更新的负信号；r286 还额外证明了 shared coarse 在当前 2048 many-tiny regime 下不是可随意去掉的。选择 `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的理由是：它仍建立在 current winning shared+PK scaffold 上，但改变的是 cleanup 语义而不是宽度/分摊比例的小插值，正符合当前“优先寻找更能降低 tail-error 的结构升级”要求。主要风险是该 family 在 1024-expert 上曾接近 dual-shared 平台，说明串联 residual shared 可能只改善均值误差而不足以改善 exceed；但若如此，本轮也能更干净地关闭 dual-shared/residual-shared 这一整片邻域。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r286 `product_key_expert_jumprelu@2048` 得到 objective=0.276391、cost=0.088623x、exceed=0.187768，说明仅扩大 PK micro-expert 容量而移除 shared coarse 仍不如 r282；shared coarse 仍是当前 winning scaffold 的有效组成。","r283-r286 已连续表明：adaptive-active、dual-shared、更轻 shared-lowrank、plain PK control 都没有把 objective 拉过 r282，后续不应继续让这些 scaffold-local follow-up 主导预算。","`residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 已在工作区落盘且历史 round_0280 完成过接线与 smoke；其兼容性已记录为直接兼容，不需要新的代码修改或 allowlist 接线。","当前 highest-value 未决问题不是 shared 是否必要，而是 shared 分支的 cleanup 语义是否还能升级；串联 residual shared bank 比并行 dual-shared 更贴近当前“shared/coarse 吃主干，后续分支做 tail cleanup”的目标。","如果该 family 在 2048 scaffold 上仍不赢，则 dual-shared / residual-shared 这一片 shared-ordering 邻域可整体下调优先级，把预算转向真正不同的结构槽位。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果该 probe 在近同成本下明显降低 exceed 并击败 r282，则下一轮只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，优先测试 `0.25 -> 0.375` 或 `0.5`，确认 residual shared cleanup 的 coarse/cleanup 分工 knee。","如果该 probe 优于 r284/r280 但仍输给 r282，则可记录为“改变 shared ordering 有一定帮助，但不足以形成 regime shift”；后续应停止 shared-ordering 邻域细扫，转向别的 scaffold-level cleanup 升级。","如果该 probe 与 r280/r284 基本持平或更差，则可更明确地下调 dual-shared / residual-shared 整片方向，把后续结构预算转向其它仍未在当前 2048 scaffold 上验证的 genuinely different upgrade。"],"reference_round":282}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:1661:research/history/logs/agent_round_0287.stdout.log:81:  10. 当前最强已验证主线是 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`：它已经说明“shared coarse 主干 + product-key tiny routed cleanup”比 plain PK 更能改善当前目标。后续应把这条线当作 winning scaffold，而不是继续把大部分预算花在 `K / STAGE1_RATIO / LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 的线性细扫上。当前更高价值的问题是：在近同成本下，什么结构升级能在保留这套 scaffold 的同时，把 low-K exceed 再明显压低。
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:1671:research/history/logs/agent_round_0287.stdout.log:256:  4. 当前最有价值的 recent 正信号不是 plain PK，而是 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`：它说明“shared coarse 主干 + product-key tiny routed cleanup”这条分工在当前 hookpoint 上确实优于 plain PK。但后续 `STAGE1_RATIO`、`K` 等局部 follow-up 基本已接近平台，`tiny factorized expert heads` 也给出强负信号。因此后续不应继续让 `K / STAGE1_RATIO / LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 的近邻细扫主导预算；更值得优先测试的是建立在这条 shared+PK scaffold 之上的同成本或近同成本结构升级，目标是更强地降低 low-K 条件下的 exceed，例如更好的 hard-token cleanup 机制、shared/coarse 表达方式升级、或真正有差异的 variable-active residual path。
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:1677:research/history/logs/agent_round_0287.stdout.log:446:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u5199\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_1(x)} \u03b1_i^{sh,1}(x) b_i^{sh,1} + \u03a3_{j\u2208S_2(r_1(x))} \u03b1_j^{sh,2}(x) b_j^{sh,2} + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(r_2(x))} \u03a3_{m\u2208S_e^\u03c4(r_2(x))} \u03b3_{e,m}(x) c_{e,m}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d r_1(x)=x-\u03a3_i \u03b1_i^{sh,1} b_i^{sh,1}\uff0cr_2(x)=r_1(x)-\u03a3_j \u03b1_j^{sh,2} b_j^{sh,2}\u3002\u4e24\u8def shared bank \u4e0e routed PK expert \u5b50\u5e93\u90fd\u4ecd\u662f\u9759\u6001\u5e93\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u53ea\u662f\u201cshared bank 1 \u67e5\u8868 -> residual -> shared bank 2 \u67e5\u8868 -> residual -> product-key \u8def\u7531\u5230\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> expert \u5185 JumpReLU sparse support -> \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\u201d\uff0c\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk`\u3001`lowrank_adaptive_budget_residual` \u7b49\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9 family \u4ecd\u53ea\u4f5c\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1ar275\u2192r279 \u5728\u540c\u4e00 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` family \u5185\u53ea\u628a objective \u4ece\u7ea6 0.2814 \u5c0f\u5e45\u538b\u5230\u7ea6 0.2806\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5e76\u884c dual-shared \u7684 split \u8f74\u5df2\u63a5\u8fd1\u5e73\u53f0\uff1b\u4e0b\u4e00\u6b65\u66f4\u503c\u5f97\u56de\u7b54\u7684\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u8865\u8fd1\u90bb `STAGE1_RATIO`\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u628a\u4e24\u4e2a shared bank \u4ece\u201c\u540c\u4e00 shared stage \u5185\u5e76\u884c\u7ade\u4e89 top-k\u201d\u6539\u6210\u201c\u4e24\u4e2a residual shared stage \u4e32\u8054\u6e05\u7406\u4e3b\u5e72\u201d\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r279 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u5207\u5230\u65b0\u5b9e\u73b0\u7684 `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32, EXPANSION_FACTOR=1, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, NUM_EXPERTS=1024, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.375, adam, LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59 recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u540c\u6210\u672c 0.109375x \u4e0b\u4fe1\u606f\u589e\u91cf\u6700\u9ad8\u7684\u65b0\u7ed3\u6784 probe\u3002\u5b83\u4e0e\u73b0\u6709 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u7684\u7cbe\u786e\u5dee\u5f02\u662f\uff1a\u65e7 family \u5728\u4e24\u8def shared bank \u4e0a\u505a\u4e00\u6b21\u8054\u5408 shared top-k\uff1b\u65b0 family \u5219\u5148\u7528\u7b2c\u4e00\u4e2a shared bank \u505a coarse reconstruction\uff0c\u518d\u8ba9\u7b2c\u4e8c\u4e2a shared bank \u53ea\u5728 residual \u4e0a\u5de5\u4f5c\uff0c\u76ee\u6807\u662f\u5728\u4e0d\u589e\u52a0 active path \u548c\u4e0d\u589e\u52a0\u6210\u672c\u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u66f4\u597d\u5730\u964d\u4f4e hard-token tail\u3002\u82e5\u8be5\u4e32\u8054 residual shared \u8bed\u4e49\u80fd\u628a exceed \u4ece r279 \u7684 0.171186 \u518d\u538b\u7ea6 0.0056 \u5230 <=0.1656\uff0c\u5c31\u6709\u673a\u4f1a\u5728\u540c\u6210\u672c\u4e0b\u53cd\u8d85\u5f53\u524d incumbent 0.275001\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:1694:research/history/logs/agent_round_0287.stdout.log:642:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i^{sh,1}(x) b_i^{sh,1} + Σ_{j∈S_2(r_1(x))} α_j^{sh,2}(x) b_j^{sh,2} + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r_2(x))} Σ_{m∈S_e^τ(r_2(x))} γ_{e,m}(x) c_{e,m}`，其中 `r_1(x)=x-Σ_i α_i^{sh,1} b_i^{sh,1}`，`r_2(x)=r_1(x)-Σ_j α_j^{sh,2} b_j^{sh,2}`。两级 shared bank 与 PK-routed expert 子库都仍是静态子库；在线链路只是“shared bank 1 查表 -> residual -> shared bank 2 查表 -> residual -> product-key 选少量静态 expert 子库 -> expert 内 JumpReLU sparse support -> 查表加权和”，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态子库有限加权和推理链路，因此 `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 判定为直接兼容。明确不兼容 family 仍只作历史参考，不能驱动当前兼容 leaderboard。本轮唯一主假设是：r286 已经用 `product_key_expert_jumprelu@2048` 证明“仅靠更细 PK micro-experts 而去掉 shared coarse”不能赢过 incumbent；因此当前更高信息量的问题不是继续做 plain PK 或 shared-lowrank 的邻域微调，而是在保留 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 这条 winning scaffold 的前提下，测试一种真正不同的 cleanup 语义。相对 r282 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 切到 `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，保持 `NUM_EXPERTS=2048, K=32, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, EXPANSION_FACTOR=1, OPTIMIZER=adam, LR=8e-4` 与其余 recipe 不变，直接回答“把第二个 shared 分支改成 residual-only cleanup，而不是并行同层 coarse 竞争，是否能在近同成本下更强地压低 low-K tail exceed”。该 family 在 1024-expert 上只做过一次早期 probe，尚未在当前 2048 many-tiny scaffold 上做过 clean matched test，因此这不是旧线回潮，而是建立在当前 best scaffold 上的结构升级 probe。","summary":"以 r282 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，在同一 2048 many-tiny scaffold 上执行一轮 matched architecture probe，直接测试“串联 residual shared cleanup + PK routed cleanup”能否比当前 incumbent 更慢地恶化 hard-token exceed。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮严格满足单变量原则：相对 r282 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。之所以不继续围绕 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 做 `K/STAGE1_RATIO/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 近邻细扫，是因为最近 4 轮都未扩展 objective，且 prompt 明确要求此时优先换结构槽位。之所以不再回到 plain PK、shared-lowrank、stacked PK、factorized expert 或更老的 routed/shared-routed 线，是因为它们已经在当前 target 给出更强或更新的负信号；r286 还额外证明了 shared coarse 在当前 2048 many-tiny regime 下不是可随意去掉的。选择 `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的理由是：它仍建立在 current winning shared+PK scaffold 上，但改变的是 cleanup 语义而不是宽度/分摊比例的小插值，正符合当前“优先寻找更能降低 tail-error 的结构升级”要求。主要风险是该 family 在 1024-expert 上曾接近 dual-shared 平台，说明串联 residual shared 可能只改善均值误差而不足以改善 exceed；但若如此，本轮也能更干净地关闭 dual-shared/residual-shared 这一整片邻域。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r286 `product_key_expert_jumprelu@2048` 得到 objective=0.276391、cost=0.088623x、exceed=0.187768，说明仅扩大 PK micro-expert 容量而移除 shared coarse 仍不如 r282；shared coarse 仍是当前 winning scaffold 的有效组成。","r283-r286 已连续表明：adaptive-active、dual-shared、更轻 shared-lowrank、plain PK control 都没有把 objective 拉过 r282，后续不应继续让这些 scaffold-local follow-up 主导预算。","`residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 已在工作区落盘且历史 round_0280 完成过接线与 smoke；其兼容性已记录为直接兼容，不需要新的代码修改或 allowlist 接线。","当前 highest-value 未决问题不是 shared 是否必要，而是 shared 分支的 cleanup 语义是否还能升级；串联 residual shared bank 比并行 dual-shared 更贴近当前“shared/coarse 吃主干，后续分支做 tail cleanup”的目标。","如果该 family 在 2048 scaffold 上仍不赢，则 dual-shared / residual-shared 这一片 shared-ordering 邻域可整体下调优先级，把预算转向真正不同的结构槽位。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果该 probe 在近同成本下明显降低 exceed 并击败 r282，则下一轮只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，优先测试 `0.25 -> 0.375` 或 `0.5`，确认 residual shared cleanup 的 coarse/cleanup 分工 knee。","如果该 probe 优于 r284/r280 但仍输给 r282，则可记录为“改变 shared ordering 有一定帮助，但不足以形成 regime shift”；后续应停止 shared-ordering 邻域细扫，转向别的 scaffold-level cleanup 升级。","如果该 probe 与 r280/r284 基本持平或更差，则可更明确地下调 dual-shared / residual-shared 整片方向，把后续结构预算转向其它仍未在当前 2048 scaffold 上验证的 genuinely different upgrade。"],"reference_round":282}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:1696:research/history/round_summaries/round_0272.json:20:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u5199\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh^{k1}(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_var-pk(r1(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e^{k2}(r1(x))} \u03b3_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d r1(x)=x-\u03a3 \u03b1_i^sh(x)b_i^sh\uff0c\u7b2c\u4e00\u9879\u662f always-on shared coarse \u9759\u6001\u5e93\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u7b2c\u4e8c\u9879\u662f\u5728 residual \u4e0a\u7531 product-key \u8def\u7531\u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u5185\u505a JumpReLU \u7a00\u758f\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u4f46 active expert \u96c6\u5408\u4e0d\u518d\u56fa\u5b9a\u4e3a 2\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u6309 router \u7f6e\u4fe1\u5ea6\u5bf9\u7b80\u5355 token \u53ea\u4fdd\u7559 1 expert\u3001\u56f0\u96be token \u4ecd\u4fdd\u7559 2 experts\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared \u67e5\u8868 -> residual -> PK \u8def\u7531\u5230\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> expert \u5185 sparse support -> \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u65b0 family `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9 family `batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk`\u3001`lowrank_adaptive_budget_residual` \u7ee7\u7eed\u53ea\u4f5c\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u53c2\u4e0e\u5f53\u524d\u517c\u5bb9 leaderboard\u3002r266 \u7ed9\u51fa\u5f53\u524d\u552f\u4e00 recent \u6b63\u4fe1\u53f7 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`\uff0c\u800c r265 \u7684 `adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\u53ea\u8bf4\u660e\u201c\u6ca1\u6709 shared coarse \u4e3b\u5e72\u65f6\uff0cvariable-active PK \u4e0d\u591f\u201d\uff0c\u5e76\u4e0d\u80fd\u88c1\u6389\u201cshared+PK + variable-active path\u201d\u8fd9\u4e2a\u66f4\u8d34\u8fd1 prompt \u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\u3002\u6700\u8fd1\u4e24\u8f6e r270/r271 \u6ca1\u6709\u628a objective \u62c9\u4f4e\uff0c\u6309\u89c4\u5219\u5e94\u4f18\u5148\u5207\u6362\u5230\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff1b\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684\u65b0\u69fd\u4f4d\u6b63\u662f\u628a recent \u6700\u5f3a\u4fe1\u53f7 `shared+PK` \u4e0e\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u672a\u51b3\u65b9\u5411 `variable-active path by difficulty` \u5408\u5e76\u3002\u8be5\u65b0 family \u5df2\u5b9e\u9645\u843d\u76d8\u5e76\u5b8c\u6210 exact-string smoke\uff1b\u672c\u5730 exact \u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u5728\u5f53\u524d many-tiny recipe `K=32, NUM_EXPERTS=1024, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` \u4e0b\uff0ccombined_accesses=401408\uff0cexact total_cost_ratio=0.095703125\uff0c\u4e0e r266 \u5b8c\u5168\u540c\u6210\u672c\u3002\u56e0\u6b64\u76f8\u5bf9 r266 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u662f\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u5e72\u51c0\u3001\u4fe1\u606f\u589e\u91cf\u6700\u9ad8\u7684\u65b0\u7ed3\u6784 probe\uff1b\u8981\u51fb\u8d25 r266 exact objective=0.275001125\uff0c\u53ea\u9700 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.179298`\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:1699:research/history/round_summaries/round_0272.json:26:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u6ee1\u8db3\u5f53\u524d round-272 \u7684\u9ed8\u8ba4\u89c4\u5219\uff1a\u6700\u8fd1\u4e24\u8f6e\u6ca1\u6709\u628a objective \u660e\u663e\u62c9\u4f4e\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4f18\u5148\u5207\u6362\u5230\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u6cbf `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u505a `K/LATENTS/STAGE1_RATIO` \u7ec6\u626b\u3002\u4e4b\u6240\u4ee5\u9009\u8fd9\u4e2a\u65b0 family\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u518d\u56de\u5230 hash\u3001PK-factorized\u3001shared-lowrank \u6216\u65e7\u7684 adaptive-active non-shared \u65b9\u5411\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u5b83\u76f4\u63a5\u627f\u63a5\u5f53\u524d\u552f\u4e00 recent \u6b63\u4fe1\u53f7 `shared+PK`\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u628a\u53d8\u5316\u5c40\u9650\u5728 prompt \u660e\u786e\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u3001\u4f46\u5c1a\u672a\u5728\u8fd9\u6761\u4e3b\u7ebf\u4e0a\u88ab\u9a8c\u8bc1\u8fc7\u7684\u201c\u6309\u96be\u5ea6\u81ea\u9002\u5e94 active path\u201d\u8fd9\u4e00\u6761\u7ed3\u6784\u8f74\u4e0a\u3002\u5de5\u7a0b\u6539\u52a8\u88ab\u9650\u5236\u5728\u5fc5\u8981\u6587\u4ef6\uff1a`sparsify/config.py`\u3001`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`\u3001`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`\uff1b\u6ca1\u6709\u65b0\u589e tunable env key\uff0c\u53ea\u662f\u4e3a\u65b0 architecture \u63a5\u901a\u73b0\u6709 expert/STAGE1/JUMPRELU \u53c2\u6570\u96c6\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f\u5f53\u524d cost proxy \u4ecd\u6309 worst-case `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` \u8ba1\u8d39\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8fd9\u8f6e\u82e5\u6210\u529f\u53ea\u80fd\u4f53\u73b0\u4e3a exceed \u6539\u5584\u800c\u975e cost \u4e0b\u964d\uff1b\u4f46\u8fd9\u6070\u597d\u8ba9\u7ed3\u6784\u5224\u65ad\u66f4\u5e72\u51c0\u3002\u5982\u679c\u8fde\u8fd9\u4e2a\u201cshared+PK \u7684\u66f4\u5f3a Expert-Choice \u53d8\u4f53\u201d\u90fd\u65e0\u6cd5\u5728 same-cost lane \u6539\u5584 objective\uff0c\u5c31\u53ef\u4ee5\u66f4\u6709\u628a\u63e1\u5730\u4e0b\u8c03 vari