research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:2199:research/history/logs/agent_round_0286.stdout.log:6668:research/history/round_summaries/round_0276.json:80:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u7b26\u5408\u5f53\u524d\u9636\u6bb5\u7ea6\u675f\u3002\u6700\u8fd1\u4e24\u8f6e r274-r275 \u90fd\u505c\u7559\u5728\u540c\u4e00 dual-shared family \u5185\uff0c\u4e14 objective \u4ecd\u672a\u63a5\u8fd1 incumbent\uff1b\u6309\u7b56\u7565\u6b64\u65f6\u5e94\u4f18\u5148\u6362\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u8865 `STAGE1_RATIO` \u8fd1\u90bb\u70b9\u3002\u9009\u62e9 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 dual-shared \u4e0a\u505a `0.125/0.375` \u5206\u88c2\u70b9\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u5b83\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5f53\u524d\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u65b9\u5411\u201cvariable-active path by difficulty\u201d\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u5b8c\u5168\u5efa\u7acb\u5728\u5df2\u6709 winning scaffold \u7684\u8fd1\u540c\u6210\u672c\u5347\u7ea7\u4e0a\u3002\u4ee3\u7801\u4fa7\u4ec5\u65b0\u589e\u6700\u5c0f family\uff0c\u5e76\u5b8c\u6210 whitelist\u3001factory dispatch\u3001override allowlist\u3001compatibility registry \u4e0e exact-string smoke\uff1b\u6ca1\u6709\u65b0\u589e tunable key\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4e0d\u9700\u8981\u6539 `config_resolution`\u3001`runner` \u6216 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f adaptive active \u5728\u5355-shared \u7248\u672c\u4e0a\u66fe\u7ed9\u8fc7\u5f31\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1b\u4f46 dual-shared scaffold \u5df2\u628a coarse \u4e3b\u5e72\u62ac\u5f3a\uff0c\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u6709\u4ef7\u503c\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u6b63\u662f\u8fd9\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u8ba9 difficulty-aware cleanup \u771f\u6b63\u53d1\u6325\u4f5c\u7528\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:2200:research/history/logs/agent_round_0286.stdout.log:6990:research/history/round_summaries/round_0270.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u5199\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(x)} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e(x)} \u03b3_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d\u7b2c\u4e00\u9879\u662f always-on shared coarse \u9759\u6001\u5e93\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u7b2c\u4e8c\u9879\u662f\u5728 product-key \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u5185\uff0c\u7528 factorized local head \u4ea7\u751f\u7cfb\u6570\u540e\u7684\u7a00\u758f\u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff1b\u4e0e `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u7684\u5dee\u5f02\u4e0d\u5728 shared/PK \u5206\u5de5\uff0c\u800c\u5728 expert \u5185\u90e8\u4ece full-dim local head \u6539\u6210 tiny factorized head\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared \u67e5\u8868 -> PK \u8def\u7531\u5230\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> expert \u5185\u5c40\u90e8 sparse support -> \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9 family `batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk`\u3001`lowrank_adaptive_budget_residual` \u7ee7\u7eed\u53ea\u4f5c\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u53c2\u4e0e\u5f53\u524d\u517c\u5bb9 leaderboard\u3002r268 \u4e0e r269 \u5df2\u628a `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u7684 split \u8f74\u57fa\u672c\u88c1\u6e05\uff1a\u5728\u5b8c\u5168\u540c exact cost 0.095703125 \u4e0b\uff0c`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` \u4f18\u4e8e `0.5` \u4e0e `0.125`\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d family \u7684\u9ad8\u4ef7\u503c\u5c40\u90e8\u5047\u8bbe\u5df2\u57fa\u672c\u6536\u655b\uff0c\u4e0d\u5e94\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u540c family \u4e0a\u7ec6\u626b\u3002\u4e0b\u4e00\u8f6e\u66f4\u6709\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u5e94\u56de\u5230\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\u3002\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u8d34\u8fd1 recent \u6b63\u4fe1\u53f7\u3001\u4e14\u4ecd\u5904\u5728 small-K \u73b0\u5b9e\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u7684\u672a\u51b3\u7ed3\u6784\u95ee\u9898\uff0c\u662f\uff1ashared+PK \u7684\u6536\u76ca\u7a76\u7adf\u6765\u81ea coarse+PK \u5206\u5de5\u672c\u8eab\uff0c\u8fd8\u662f full-dim expert head \u5fc5\u4e0d\u53ef\u5c11\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r266 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301\u5f53\u524d many-tiny recipe `K=32, NUM_EXPERTS=1024, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56` \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u88c1\u51b3\u201cshared coarse + PK routing + tiny factorized experts\u201d\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u3002\u672c\u5730 exact \u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5 recipe \u7684 combined_accesses=485376\uff0cexact total_cost_ratio=0.11572265625\uff0c\u4ecd\u5728\u73b0\u5b9e\u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u5185\uff1b\u82e5\u8981\u51fb\u8d25 r266 exact objective=0.275001125\uff0c\u53ea\u9700 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.15927846875`\u3002\u8fd9\u95e8\u69db\u867d\u7136\u4e0d\u4f4e\uff0c\u4f46\u6bd4 0.19x family \u9700\u8981\u7684 `exceed<0.09` \u66f4\u73b0\u5b9e\uff0c\u800c\u4e14\u80fd\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u5f53\u524d prompt \u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u7684 \u2018tiny experts / lighter local head\u2019 \u7ed3\u6784\u95ee\u9898\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:2204:research/history/logs/agent_round_0286.stdout.log:7087:research/history/logs/agent_action_0277.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j}(r_sh(x)) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是低秩 shared bottleneck，{b_i^sh} 是静态 shared coarse 子库，r_sh(x)=x-Σ_i α_i^sh b_i^sh，{B_e} 是静态 PK-routed expert 子库，E_pk(·) 由 low-rank hidden 上的 left/right product-key 路由选出少量 experts，JumpReLU 只改变 expert 内局部 support。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared coarse 子库查表 + PK expert 选择 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，不依赖动态字典，因此该 family 判定为直接兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：相对 r263 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `product_key_expert_jumprelu` 切到新 family `shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，保持 `K=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=1024`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余 recipe 不变，用廉价 low-rank shared coarse branch 替代 plain PK 的无 shared 主干，同时保留 full-expert PK cleanup，能够在 exact `total_cost_ratio=0.0816802978515625` 的近同成本档位比 r263/r266 更有效地压低 exceed_alpha_0.50，并形成更有价值的新 objective 点。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该 family 在约 `0.08168x` 下明显优于 r263 并接近或击败 r266，下一轮应留在该 family，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=32`，测试 shared bottleneck 是否还能进一步降 cost 而不明显抬高 exceed。","如果该 family 只比 plain PK 小幅更好但仍明显输给 incumbent，则记录为“shared low-rank coarse + PK cleanup` 有一定价值，但 shared coarse 的表达力仍不够”，后续不要在这条线做低信息细扫。","如果该 family 明显失败，则可更有把握地下调“shared low-rank coarse + PK cleanup”优先级，把预算转回其他真正改变 tail cleanup 语义的结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，真实改动文件为 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`、`research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md`。","该 family 与 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：always-on shared branch 从 full `d_in -> latents` sparse encoder 改为 low-rank bottleneck `h(x)=ReLU(Bx)` 上的 factorized shared coarse head；与 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` 的精确差异是：只有 shared coarse 与 PK routing 走低秩 hidden，routed expert cleanup 仍保留 full `d_in -> latents_per_expert` expert encoders，而不是 factorized expert heads。","为了避免继承自 reference 配置的 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 把成本抬回旧的高成本负信号区，本实现将 shared hidden 维度限制为 `min(FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT)`；在当前 recipe 下实际 hidden_dim=56。","exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu', k=32, expansion_factor=1, stage1_ratio=0.25, factorized_hidden_dim=256, num_experts=1024, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56)` 可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'ARCHITECTURE', value:'shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu'}], fallback_architecture='shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu')` 返回 `[]`。","本地 exact 成本复核：selection_accesses=178752 (`0.0426177978515625x`)、deployment_accesses=163840 (`0.0390625x`)、combined_accesses=342592 (`0.0816802978515625x`)；这比 dual-shared / lowrank-trunk 线更轻，几乎回到 plain PK 的成本档位。","兼容性注册表已补充该 family，当前解析结果为 `direct_compatible`；更新后本地计数为直接兼容 15 个、扩展兼容 25 个、不兼容 3 个。","在该 exact 成本档位，若想击败 r263 objective=0.27600582122802736，所需 exceed 门槛约为 `0.19432552337646484`；若想击败 incumbent r266 objective=0.275001，则所需 exceed 门槛约为 `0.1933207021484375`。"],"reference_round":263,"self_review":"这轮符合当前运行优先级。r274-r276 已经在 dual-shared scaffold 上连续给出不够强的 objective 信号，其中 r275 虽有正向 exceed 改善，但仍未接近 incumbent，而 r276 的 adaptive 变体又回退；按规则此时应优先换结构槽位，而不是继续在同一 scaffold 上做 split/active-path 邻域细扫。选择 `shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 而不是继续堆 dual-shared 变体，是因为它更直接对应当前高优先级方向“shared bottleneck + expert-specific head”，同时保留当前已验证有效的 PK cleanup 语义，并且本地 exact cost 复核落在 `~0.08x`，明显优于 `shared_lowrank_*` 旧家族在当前 1024-expert recipe 下的 `~0.19x` 高成本负信号。代码侧只新增最小 family，并完成 whitelist、factory dispatch、override allowlist、compatibility registry 与 exact-string smoke；没有新增 tunable env key，因此不需要改 `config_resolution`、`runner` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。主要风险是低秩 shared bottleneck 可能过弱，shared coarse 只是在 cost 上更左却换不回足够的 exceed 改善；但这正是一个高信息量、近同成本的新结构 probe。","summary":"已新增并接通 `shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。建议以 r263 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 做一轮 matched architecture probe，直接裁决“廉价 low-rank shared coarse + full-expert PK cleanup”能否在 `0.08168x` 的低成本档位把 objective 真正压低。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:2205:research/history/logs/agent_round_0286.stdout.log:7108:research/history/logs/agent_action_0270.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式写为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中第一项是 always-on shared coarse 静态库的有限加权和，第二项是在 product-key 选出的少量静态 expert 子库内，用 factorized local head 产生系数后的稀疏查表加权和；与 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的差异不在 shared/PK 分工，而在 expert 内部从 full-dim local head 改成 tiny factorized head。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“shared 查表 -> PK 路由到静态 expert 子库 -> expert 内局部 sparse support -> 查表加权和 -> 选择性补偿”，不涉及动态字典生成，因此 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容；不兼容 family `batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk`、`lowrank_adaptive_budget_residual` 继续只作历史参考，不参与当前兼容 leaderboard。r268 与 r269 已把 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的 split 轴基本裁清：在完全同 exact cost 0.095703125 下，`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 优于 `0.5` 与 `0.125`，说明当前 family 的高价值局部假设已基本收敛，不应继续在同 family 上细扫。下一轮更有信息量的问题应回到新的结构槽位。当前最贴近 recent 正信号、且仍处在 small-K 现实成本带的未决结构问题，是：shared+PK 的收益究竟来自 coarse+PK 分工本身，还是 full-dim expert head 必不可少。相对 r266 只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk`，保持当前 many-tiny recipe `K=32, NUM_EXPERTS=1024, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56` 不变，可直接裁决“shared coarse + PK routing + tiny factorized experts”是否值得继续。本地 exact 成本复核显示该 recipe 的 combined_accesses=485376，exact total_cost_ratio=0.11572265625，仍在现实主战场内；若要击败 r266 exact objective=0.275001125，只需 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.15927846875`。这门槛虽然不低，但比 0.19x family 需要的 `exceed<0.09` 更现实，而且能直接回答当前 prompt 高优先级的 ‘tiny experts / lighter local head’ 结构问题。","summary":"切到新的 matched architecture probe：以 r266 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk`。目标是在保留当前最强 recent 结构分工 shared+PK 的前提下，直接测试把 full expert heads 压成 tiny factorized heads 后，objective 是否还能继续下降。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮遵守单变量原则，相对 r266 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。之所以不继续留在 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 做 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT/K` 局部补点，是因为最近两轮已经把该 family 最核心的 split 假设裁得很清楚：更重或更轻的 shared coarse 都更差，继续细扫的信息增量很低，不符合当前默认应切换结构槽位的规则。之所以选 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` 而不是 `shared_lowrank_*`、`factorized_router_expert_topk` 或再回 `hashed_expert_jumprelu`，是因为它最直接承接当前唯一 recent 正信号 `shared+PK`，同时把变化局限在 expert 内部头部表达能力这一条高价值结构轴上；而 shared-lowrank 系列在当前 target 的 small-K lane 已有多次强负信号，hash 与 plain PK-factorized 也已有更直接的坏迹象。主要风险是 factorized local head 会像 r259 那样严重伤害 exceed；但 r259 建立在 128-bank/192-width 的不同容量组织上，本轮 many-tiny 1024-bank/56-width 的 clean re-test 仍有结构信息价值。如果它仍明显失败，就可以更果断地下调“tiny factorized experts”在当前 hookpoint 上的优先级。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r268 与 r269 已把 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的 split 轴基本裁清：在 exact 同成本 0.095703125 下，`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 优于 `0.5` 与 `0.125`；shared+PK family 仍值得保留，但这条局部轴不应再继续主导预算。","当前 ~0.10x 成本带的 best recent exact objective 仍是 r266 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，objective=0.275001125；r267 AE=3、r268 stage1=0.5、r269 stage1=0.125 都更差。","本地 exact 成本复核：`shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk K=32 NUM_EXPERTS=1024 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 的 combined_accesses=485376，exact total_cost_ratio=0.11572265625；`product_key_factorized_expert_topk` 同 recipe 为 471040 / 0.1123046875。","历史上 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` 与 `product_key_factorized_expert_topk` 在旧的 128-bank/192-width 配方下给过强负信号（r259/r260），但尚未在当前 many-tiny 1024-bank/56-width recipe 上做过 clean matched probe。","不兼容 family 继续不得驱动当前兼容 leaderboard 与主线决策：`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk`、`lowrank_adaptive_budget_residual`。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` 在当前 many-tiny recipe 下能把 exceed 压到约 0.159 或更低，则说明 recent 正信号主要来自 shared+PK 的分工与组合路由，而不是 full-dim local head 本身；后续可留在该 family，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 继续确认 tiny-expert 压缩边界。","如果该 probe 仍像 r259 那样明显失败，则可以较清晰判定当前 hookpoint 上 full expert heads 仍是 shared+PK 成功的必要条件，后续不应再把预算花在 factorized-expert 变体上。","如果该 family 只小幅劣于 r266，但远好于旧的 r259/r260，则说明 many-tiny 组织方式确实部分缓解了 factorized experts 的问题；那时更合理的下一问将是 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` 的 hidden-dim/width knee，而不是再回到 hash 或 shared-lowrank 旧槽位。"],"reference_round":266}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:2206:research/history/logs/agent_round_0286.stdout.log:7109:research/history/logs/agent_action_0271.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh^{k1}(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r1(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^{k2}(r1(x))} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 r1(x)=x-Σ α_i^sh(x)b_i^sh，shared coarse 分支与 product-key routed expert cleanup 都是静态子库上的有限加权和。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“shared 查表 -> residual -> PK 路由到静态 expert 子库 -> expert 内 sparse support -> 查表加权和 -> 选择性补偿”，不涉及动态字典生成，因此 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 继续判定为直接兼容；不兼容 family `batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk`、`lowrank_adaptive_budget_residual` 仍只作历史参考，不参与当前兼容 leaderboard。r268/r269 已把该 family 的 `STAGE1_RATIO` 轴基本裁清，r270 又强烈否定了把当前 recent 正信号压成 tiny factorized experts 的方向，说明当前 highest-value 未决问题不再是同 family 的 split 细节，也不是继续切新 family 做低胜率探针，而是这个唯一 recent 正信号能否通过更高一点的 deploy budget 真正换回足够的 exceed 改善。相对 r266 只改 `K=48`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu, NUM_EXPERTS=1024, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 不变，是当前最干净的容量 knee probe。本地 exact 成本复核：`K=48` 时 selection 仍为 237568，deployment 为 245760，combined_accesses=483328，exact total_cost_ratio=0.115234375；要击败 r266 exact objective=0.275001125，只需 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.15976675`。这比 `K=64` 所需的 `<0.1402355` 现实得多，也比 `K=40` 更像真正有信息量的容量测试。","summary":"回到当前唯一有 recent 正信号的 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，以 r266 为 reference 只改 `K=48`，做一轮 shared+PK 在 many-tiny recipe 下的容量 knee probe。目标是判断稍高 deploy budget 是否能把 exceed 真正压到足以刷新当前 best exact objective。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮遵守单变量原则，相对 r266 只改 `K`。虽然最近两轮没有把 objective 再往下推，但其中一轮已经按规则切到了新结构槽位 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk`，且给出了极强负信号；在这种情况下，直接继续切到另一个已多次负面的 family，信息增量并不比把当前唯一 recent 正信号做一次真正的容量 knee probe 更高。选择 `K=48` 而不是 `K=40/64` 的原因是：`K=40` 只需要约 0.0098 的 exceed 改善，过于接近小修小补；`K=64` 则需要约 0.039 的 exceed 改善，门槛偏硬。`K=48` 处在更合理的中间档，既是明确的容量测试，又仍保留现实赢面。主要风险是 exceed 下降幅度不足以覆盖额外 deployment 成本，导致 objective 仍不如 r266；但如果如此，也能更清晰地说明当前 shared+PK 线在 `K=32` 附近已经接近局部 knee，后续应回到新的结构槽位而不是继续沿 K 轴上探。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"48"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r270 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` 在当前 many-tiny 1024-bank/56-width recipe 下给出极强负信号：objective=0.500349，cost=0.115723，exceed=0.384626，且训练曲线 `curve_still_improving=false`；这基本否定了当前 hookpoint 上的 tiny factorized experts 方向。","`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的 split 轴已基本收敛：r266 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 优于 r268 `0.5` 与 r269 `0.125`，因此后续不应继续在该轴上消耗预算。","本地 exact 成本复核：`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 在 `K=40/48/64`、其余维持 r266 recipe 时 selection 都是 237568；deployment 分别为 204800/245760/327680；combined_accesses 分别为 442368/483328/565248，对应 exact total_cost_ratio 约 0.10546875/0.115234375/0.134765625。","在当前 recent 证据里，best exact objective 仍是 r266 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`：objective=0.275001125，cost=0.095703125，exceed=0.179298；r267/r268/r269/r270 都更差。","不兼容 family 继续不得驱动当前兼容 leaderboard 与主线决策：`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk`、`lowrank_adaptive_budget_residual`。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=48` 能把 exceed 压到约 0.160 以下并刷新 r266，则说明当前 shared+PK line 仍有可用的容量延展空间；下一轮应留在该 family，只判断 `K=64` 是否还有继续下降 objective 的现实可能。","如果 `K=48` 只带来很小的 exceed 改善，无法覆盖额外 deploy 成本，则说明当前 shared+PK line 在 `K=32` 附近已经接近局部 objective knee，后续应停止沿 K 轴继续上探并切回新的结构槽位。","如果 `K=48` 的训练曲线明显更稳、但最终 objective 仍略输给 r266，则说明当前 family 的收益更多来自 early/mid-stage 拟合而不是 tail exceed 真正收敛；那时应优先探索新的结构机制，而不是继续做 family 内插值。"],"reference_round":266}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:2208:research/history/logs/agent_round_0286.stdout.log:7120:research/history/round_summaries/round_0270.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u5199\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(x)} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e(x)} \u03b3_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d\u7b2c\u4e00\u9879\u662f always-on shared coarse \u9759\u6001\u5e93\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u7b2c\u4e8c\u9879\u662f\u5728 product-key \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u5185\uff0c\u7528 factorized local head \u4ea7\u751f\u7cfb\u6570\u540e\u7684\u7a00\u758f\u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff1b\u4e0e `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u7684\u5dee\u5f02\u4e0d\u5728 shared/PK \u5206\u5de5\uff0c\u800c\u5728 expert \u5185\u90e8\u4ece full-dim local head \u6539\u6210 tiny factorized head\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared \u67e5\u8868 -> PK \u8def\u7531\u5230\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> expert \u5185\u5c40\u90e8 sparse support -> \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9 family `batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk`\u3001`lowrank_adaptive_budget_residual` \u7ee7\u7eed\u53ea\u4f5c\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u53c2\u4e0e\u5f53\u524d\u517c\u5bb9 leaderboard\u3002r268 \u4e0e r269 \u5df2\u628a `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u7684 split \u8f74\u57fa\u672c\u88c1\u6e05\uff1a\u5728\u5b8c\u5168\u540c exact cost 0.095703125 \u4e0b\uff0c`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` \u4f18\u4e8e `0.5` \u4e0e `0.125`\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d family \u7684\u9ad8\u4ef7\u503c\u5c40\u90e8\u5047\u8bbe\u5df2\u57fa\u672c\u6536\u655b\uff0c\u4e0d\u5e94\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u540c family \u4e0a\u7ec6\u626b\u3002\u4e0b\u4e00\u8f6e\u66f4\u6709\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u5e94\u56de\u5230\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\u3002\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u8d34\u8fd1 recent \u6b63\u4fe1\u53f7\u3001\u4e14\u4ecd\u5904\u5728 small-K \u73b0\u5b9e\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u7684\u672a\u51b3\u7ed3\u6784\u95ee\u9898\uff0c\u662f\uff1ashared+PK \u7684\u6536\u76ca\u7a76\u7adf\u6765\u81ea coarse+PK \u5206\u5de5\u672c\u8eab\uff0c\u8fd8\u662f full-dim expert head \u5fc5\u4e0d\u53ef\u5c11\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r266 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301\u5f53\u524d many-tiny recipe `K=32, NUM_EXPERTS=1024, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56` \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u88c1\u51b3\u201cshared coarse + PK routing + tiny factorized experts\u201d\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u3002\u672c\u5730 exact \u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5 recipe \u7684 combined_accesses=485376\uff0cexact total_cost_ratio=0.11572265625\uff0c\u4ecd\u5728\u73b0\u5b9e\u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u5185\uff1b\u82e5\u8981\u51fb\u8d25 r266 exact objective=0.275001125\uff0c\u53ea\u9700 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.15927846875`\u3002\u8fd9\u95e8\u69db\u867d\u7136\u4e0d\u4f4e\uff0c\u4f46\u6bd4 0.19x family \u9700\u8981\u7684 `exceed<0.09` \u66f4\u73b0\u5b9e\uff0c\u800c\u4e14\u80fd\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u5f53\u524d prompt \u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u7684 \u2018tiny experts / lighter local head\u2019 \u7ed3\u6784\u95ee\u9898\u3002",
