research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:2231:research/history/logs/agent_round_0286.stdout.log:7726:research/history/round_summaries/round_0282.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(r_sh(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e^\u03c4(r_sh(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `{b_i^sh}` \u662f always-on shared coarse \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`{b_{e,j}}` \u662f product-key \u8def\u7531\u5230\u7684\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff0c\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared \u67e5\u8868 -> residual -> PK \u9009\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> expert \u5185 JumpReLU sparse support -> \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r266 \u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u6539 `NUM_EXPERTS=2048`\uff0c\u5176\u4f59 `K=32, EF=1, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` \u4fdd\u6301\u4e0d\u53d8\uff1b\u8fd9\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u626b `K/STAGE1_RATIO/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` \u7684\u4f4e\u4fe1\u606f\u90bb\u57df\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5 DeepSeekMoE \u98ce\u683c\u7684\u201c\u66f4\u7ec6\u7c92\u5ea6 routed micro-experts\u201d\u80fd\u5426\u5728\u76f8\u540c\u77ed active path\u3001\u76f8\u540c deployment K \u4e0b\uff0c\u7528\u66f4\u5927\u7684\u9759\u6001 routed \u5bb9\u91cf\u628a hard-token exceed \u538b\u4f4e\u3002\u5f53\u524d scaffold \u7684\u6700\u65b0\u7ed3\u6784\u5347\u7ea7 r281 \u5df2\u8bf4\u660e\u201c\u66f4\u6df1\u7684\u540c expert-set cleanup\u201d\u4e0d\u591f\uff1b\u4e0b\u4e00\u6b65\u66f4\u6709\u4ef7\u503c\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u662f expert \u5206\u7247\u7c92\u5ea6\u672c\u8eab\u662f\u5426\u624d\u662f\u74f6\u9888\u3002\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\uff1a`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu K=32 NUM_EXPERTS=2048 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` \u7684 `selection_accesses=265216`\u3001`deployment_accesses=163840`\u3001`combined_accesses=429056`\u3001`exact total_cost_ratio=0.102294921875`\uff0c\u4ecd\u7a33\u5b9a\u4f4d\u4e8e\u5f53\u524d `0.08~0.14` \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u5185\u3002\u8981\u6253\u8d62 r266 \u7684 exact objective\u22480.275001\uff0c\u53ea\u9700\u628a `exceed_alpha_0.50` \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 `0.172706` \u4ee5\u4e0b\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:2246:research/history/logs/agent_round_0286.stdout.log:7865:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式写为 `x_hat = Σ_{e∈E_pk(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`。其中 `{b_{e,j}}` 是静态 expert 子库原子，`E_pk(x)` 由两路 product-key router 选出少量 experts，expert 内再用 JumpReLU 形成局部 support；导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“product-key 选择少量静态 expert 子库 -> expert 内 sparse support -> 查表加权和 -> 选择性在线补偿”的静态子库有限加权和链路，因此 `product_key_expert_jumprelu` 判定为直接兼容。相对 r282 本轮只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 切到 `product_key_expert_jumprelu`，保持 `NUM_EXPERTS=2048, K=32, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, EXPANSION_FACTOR=1, OPTIMIZER=adam, LR=8e-4` 不变，做一个 clean matched control probe：最近 2048-scaffold 上的 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`、`dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`、`shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 都没把 objective 拉低，当前更高信息量的问题是 incumbent 的收益到底来自 always-on shared coarse 主干本身，还是主要来自 2048 many-tiny PK capacity。已有本地成本复核显示该 2048 plain-PK recipe 的 total_cost_ratio 约为 `0.09x`，低于当前 incumbent 的 `0.10x`；如果 exceed_alpha_0.50 能压到约 `0.18` 左右，就有机会在单目标上逼近或击败当前 best。明确不兼容 family 仍只作历史参考，不能驱动当前兼容t_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"风险在于 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 先前已给过负信号，而且当前 cost proxy 对 adaptive path 的计费与 dual_shared PK 基本相同，因此这轮几乎完全是在赌 exceed 改善。如果 exceed 仍停留在 `~0.16+`，这条线就不值得继续主导预算。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["本地 exact-string smoke 已通过：`dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 在 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=1024, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.375` 下可实例化并 forward/backward。","本地 cost 估计（以 r279 配置为 anchor）：selection_ratio≈0.07，deployment_ratio≈0.04，total_cost_ratio≈0.11，与 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 同量级。","`dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 尚未在当前 target 上得到真实 objective 证据；本轮的价值在于回答 variable-active cleanup 接到 dual shared scaffold 上是否值得继续。"],"next_hypotheses":["若本轮在近同成本下把 exceed 明显压到 `<=0.15` 一带，再以本 family 为 anchor 单变量检查 `NUM_EXPERTS 1024→2048` 是否能继续放缓 hard-token exceed。","若本轮 objective 仍不优于 incumbent，说明现有 adaptive-active 语义不足以改善 low-K tradeoff，后续应转向真正新的 cleanup 机制，而不是继续扫 adaptive path 邻域。","若本轮出现运行异常或配置不符，优先核对 round config / checkpoint config 中 architecture 是否确实写成 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，不要把无效轮次当结构证据。"],"reference_round":279}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4173:research/history/logs/agent_round_0297.stdout.log:1541:research/history/logs/agent_round_0276.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{s=1..2} Σ_{i∈S_s^{k1}(x)} α_{s,i}^{sh}(x) b_{s,i}^{sh} + Σ_{e∈E_pk^*(r_sh(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^{τ,k2}(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j}(r_sh(x)) b_{e,j}，其中 {B_s^sh} 是两个 always-on shared 静态子库，r_sh(x)=x-Σ_sΣ_i α_{s,i}^{sh}(x)b_{s,i}^{sh}，E_pk^*(·) 表示在 residual 上由 product-key router 按 token 难度自适应启用 1 或 2 个静态 expert 子库，JumpReLU 只改变 expert 内局部 support。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared coarse 子库查表 + residual 上的 PK 路由 + 少量 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，不依赖动态字典，因此该 family 判定为直接兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：相对 r275 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 切到新 family `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，保持 `K=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=1024`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余 recipe 不变，在 exact 同成本 `total_cost_ratio=0.109375` 下引入 difficulty-aware variable-active cleanup path，能比固定 AE=2 的 dual-shared scaffold 更有效地处理 hard tokens，把 exceed_alpha_0.50 继续从 r275 的 `0.172059` 往下压，并争取逼近或击败 incumbent r266。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该 family 在同成本下明显优于 r275，并接近或击败 r266，则下一轮只改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.125`，测试在 adaptive cleanup 存在时是否重新回到更轻 coarse split 更优。","如果该 family 只比 r275 小幅更好但仍明显不够接近 incumbent，则记录为“variable-active path 有帮助，但不足以带来 regime shift”，后续应停止在 adaptive 邻域细扫。","如果该 family 不如 r275，则说明在当前 PK/shared scaffold 上 adaptive 1-or-2 expert path 不是主要突破口，后续应转向其他真正改变 cleanup 语义或 coarse 表达方式的新结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，真实改动文件为 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`、`research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md`。","该 family 与 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：shared coarse 分支仍保持双 shared banks，但 routed cleanup 从固定 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 改为按 token 难度自适应启用 1 或 2 个 PK experts；与 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：shared coarse 容量从 1 个 shared bank 扩到 2 个。","exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu', k=32, expansion_factor=1, stage1_ratio=0.25, num_experts=1024, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56)` 可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'ARCHITECTURE', value:'dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu'}], fallback_architecture='dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu')` 返回 `[]`。","本地 exact 成本复核：selection_accesses=294912 (`0.0703125x`)、deployment_accesses=163840 (`0.0390625x`)、combined_accesses=458752 (`0.109375x`)；与 r274/r275 的 dual-shared fixed-AE scaffold 同档，因此这是一个干净的 matched architecture probe。","兼容性注册表已补充该 family，当前解析结果为 `direct_compatible`；更新后本地计数为直接兼容 14 个、扩展兼容 25 个、不兼容 3 个。","当前 dual-shared scaffold 已给出真实正向证据：r275 相对 r274 在同成本下把 exceed 从 `0.177462` 压到 `0.172059`，说明这条新 scaffold 仍值得一次 architecture-level upgrade，而不是继续做 split 邻域细扫。"],"reference_round":275,"self_review":"这轮符合当前阶段约束。最近两轮 r274-r275 都停留在同一 dual-shared family 内，且 objective 仍未接近 incumbent；按策略此时应优先换结构槽位，而不是继续补 `STAGE1_RATIO` 近邻点。选择 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 而不是继续在 dual-shared 上做 `0.125/0.375` 分裂点，是因为它直接测试当前高优先级方向“variable-active path by difficulty”，同时完全建立在已有 winning scaffold 的近同成本升级上。代码侧仅新增最小 family，并完成 whitelist、factory dispatch、override allowlist、compatibility registry 与 exact-string smoke；没有新增 tunable key，因此不需要改 `config_resolution`、`runner` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。主要风险是 adaptive active 在单-shared 版本上曾给过弱负信号；但 dual-shared scaffold 已把 coarse 主干抬强，当前最有价值的问题正是这是否能让 difficulty-aware cleanup 真正发挥作用。","summary":"已新增并接通 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。建议以 r275 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 做一轮 matched architecture probe，直接裁决“更厚 shared coarse 主干 + 按难度可变 1-or-2 PK cleanup path”能否在与 dual-shared fixed-AE 完全同成本的 `0.109375x` 档位继续显著压低 exceed。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"]}
