research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4633:research/history/logs/agent_round_0300.stdout.log:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r1(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r1(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res^τ(r2(x))} γ_m(x) c_m`，其中 `r1(x)=x-Σ_i α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh`，`r2(x)=r1(x)-Σ_{e,j} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`；`{b_i^sh}` 是 always-on shared coarse 静态子库，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 product-key 路由到的静态 expert 子库，`{c_m}` 是 tiny residual 静态子库，而最后一段 residual 系数 `γ_m(x)` 使用 JumpReLU-gated residual scorer。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时，在线链路仍是“shared 查表 -> PK expert 子库查表 -> JumpReLU residual 子库查表 -> 有限加权和 -> 选择性在线补偿”，不涉及动态字典生成，因此该 family 判定为 `扩展兼容`。`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`、`product_key_expert_jumprelu`、`dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 等兼容 family 仍可参与当前 objective leaderboard；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 只能作为历史参考，不能驱动后续决策。本轮唯一主假设是：在连续两轮 `NUM_EXPERTS` 扩容已显示 3072 有限正信号、4096 明显回撤之后，当前 low-K 主瓶颈更像是 hard-token tail cleanup 语义，而不是继续扩 routed bank 粒度；因此应切换结构槽位，而不是继续在 incumbent family 上做近邻插值。相对 r282 只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`，其余 `K=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=2048`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 保持不变，直接测试“在 winning shared+PK scaffold 上，把最终 tiny residual cleanup 从 plain residual 语义换成 JumpReLU-gated tail cleanup”能否更有效压低 `exceed_alpha_0.50`。本地精确成本自检显示该点 `selection_accesses=325696`、`deployment_accesses=163840`、`combined_accesses=489536`、`exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`，满足预算；若要击败当前 incumbent `objective=0.2684179902076721`，需要把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到 `0.1517035126686096` 以下。","summary":"建议以 r282 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`。这轮不是继续做 incumbent 邻域扫参，而是在当前最强 shared+PK scaffold 上做一次 matched cleanup-semantics probe，直接判断 JumpReLU tail residual 能否在约 `0.1167x` 成本下把 exceed 明显压低。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮严格满足单变量原则：相对 r282 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。它也符合当前 round 300 的策略要求：最近两轮已经是同一 family 上的局部延伸且没有实质击穿 incumbent，因此本轮应优先换结构槽位，而不是继续做 `NUM_EXPERTS/K/STAGE1_RATIO` 近邻细扫。之所以选择这个 family，而不是再新开一个未注册 family，是因为它已经真实落盘、已完成 whitelist/factory/allowlist/smoke/cost 检查，并且当前本地 policy 校验已通过；r297 的失败只是当时全局 incubation 满额，而不是此 family 自身不可运行。主要风险是 JumpReLU 过度抑制 tiny residual bank，导致 tail cleanup 容量下降，结果不如 r292 的 plain residual；但这正是本轮要用一个最小结构切换清晰回答的问题。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual` 已在更早轮次真实落盘并完成注册，实际修改文件是 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`；本轮无需再做代码编辑。","该 family 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是静态 shared 子库 + 静态 PK expert 子库 + 静态 residual 子库上的有限加权和，兼容性标签应记为 `扩展兼容`。","本地 exact-string smoke、override allowlist 和成本自检都已通过；当前 recipe 下 `exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`。","r297 被 `policy_reject` 的原因仅是当时新 family 进入 incubating 时撞上 incubation 上限，不是 wiring 或兼容性错误；当前用本地 `validate_action(...)` 对同一 `ARCHITECTURE` param_only 提案复核已通过。","r298 与 r299 共同说明 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 上继续扩 `NUM_EXPERTS` 已接近 knee：3072 有限正信号，但 4096 已明显回撤，因此当前更该测试 cleanup 语义升级。","若本轮结果仍不能优于 r292 的 same-cost plain residual 版本，则 shared+PK 后接 tiny residual cleanup 这整条邻域应整体降级，不再继续细扫 residual 语义。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 `0.1167x` 成本下明显优于 r292，并接近或击败 incumbent，则下一轮留在该 family，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，校准 shared coarse 与 JumpReLU tail cleanup 的预算分工。","如果该点优于 r292 但仍未赢 incumbent，则说明 cleanup 语义升级方向成立但交换率仍不足；下一轮优先只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 向左探一格，尝试回收部分 cost 而保留 exceed 收益。","如果该点与 r292 持平或更差，则说明当前瓶颈不在 residual gating 语义；后续应停止沿 shared+PK+tiny-residual 邻域继续细扫，转向别的 scaffold-level cleanup 或 coarse 表达升级。"],"reference_round":282}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4637:research/history/logs/agent_round_0300.stdout.log:457:      "design_hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u8bbe\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(r1(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e^\u03c4(r1(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + \u03a3_{m\u2208S_res^\u03c4(r2(x))} \u03b3_m(x) c_m`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `r1(x)=x-\u03a3_i \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh`\uff0c`r2(x)=r1(x)-\u03a3_{e,j} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`\uff1b`{b_i^sh}` \u662f always-on shared \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`{b_{e,j}}` \u662f PK \u8def\u7531\u5230\u7684\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`{c_m}` \u662f tiny factorized residual \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c\u6700\u540e\u4e00\u6bb5\u7cfb\u6570 `\u03b3_m(x)` \u6539\u4e3a JumpReLU-gated residual scorer\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u65f6\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared \u67e5\u8868 -> PK expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 -> JumpReLU residual \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 -> \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\uff1b\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9 family \u4ecd\u4e0d\u5f97\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u5f53\u524d shared+PK scaffold \u7684\u4e3b\u8981\u7f3a\u53e3\u5728 hard-token tail cleanup\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f shared bank \u6570\u91cf\u6216 adaptive-active \u8f7b\u5fae\u63d2\u503c\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r282 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, OPTIMIZER=adam, LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59 recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u201c\u628a\u6700\u7ec8 tiny residual cleanup \u4ece plain factorized top-k \u6539\u6210 thresholded JumpReLU residual\u201d\u80fd\u5426\u5728\u8fd1\u540c\u6210\u672c\u4e0b\u66f4\u5f3a\u538b\u4f4e `exceed_alpha_0.50`\u3002\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u81ea\u68c0\u663e\u793a\u8be5 family \u5728\u5f53\u524d recipe \u4e0b `selection_accesses=325696`\u3001`deployment_accesses=163840`\u3001`combined_accesses=489536`\u3001`exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3\u9884\u7b97\uff1b\u82e5\u60f3\u51fb\u8d25\u5f53\u524d incumbent `objective=0.2684179902076721`\uff0c\u9700\u8981\u628a `exceed_alpha_0.50` \u538b\u5230 `0.1517035126686096` \u4ee5\u4e0b\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4638:research/history/logs/agent_round_0300.stdout.log:473:      "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u8bbe\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(r_1(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e^\u03c4(r_1(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + \u03a3_{m\u2208S_res(r_2(x))} \u03b3_m(x) c_m`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `r_1(x)=x-\u03a3_i \u03b1_i^sh b_i^sh`\uff0c`r_2(x)=r_1(x)-\u03a3_{e,j} \u03b1_{e,j} b_{e,j}`\u3002\u7b2c\u4e00\u9879\u662f always-on shared coarse \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c\u7b2c\u4e8c\u9879\u662f\u5728\u6b8b\u5dee\u4e0a\u7531 product-key \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u5185\u7684 JumpReLU cleanup\uff0c\u7b2c\u4e09\u9879\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u5f88\u5c0f\u7684 factorized global residual \u9759\u6001\u5e93\u505a tail cleanup\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared \u67e5\u8868 -> residual -> PK expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 -> residual -> tiny factorized residual \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 -> \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u4f9d\u8d56\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u65b0 family `shared_product_key_expert_residual` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u660e\u786e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9 family \u4ecd\u53ea\u4f5c\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u5f97\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d\u517c\u5bb9 leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1ar283-r287 \u5df2\u57fa\u672c\u5426\u5b9a\u73b0\u6709 `shared+PK` \u90bb\u57df\u91cc\u7684 adaptive-active\u3001dual-shared\u3001residual-shared\u3001shared-lowrank \u4e0e plain-PK control\uff0c\u4f46\u8fd9\u4e9b\u5931\u8d25\u4e3b\u8981\u8bf4\u660e\u65e7 cleanup \u8bed\u4e49\u6ca1\u6709\u5f62\u6210 regime shift\uff1b\u5f53\u524d\u66f4\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u662f\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u7559 winning scaffold `shared coarse + PK routed cleanup` \u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u989d\u5916\u52a0\u4e00\u4e2a\u5f88\u5c0f\u7684\u5168\u5c40 residual tail-cleanup \u5e93\uff0c\u80fd\u5426\u628a hard-token exceed \u518d\u538b\u4e0b\u53bb\u3002\u65b0 family \u76f8\u5bf9\u73b0\u6709 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u7684\u7cbe\u786e\u5dee\u5f02\u4e0d\u662f\u91cd\u547d\u540d\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u5728 shared coarse \u4e0e PK cleanup \u4e4b\u540e\u65b0\u589e\u4e00\u4e2a tiny factorized residual bank\uff1b\u5b83\u4e5f\u4e0d\u540c\u4e8e\u5df2\u5931\u8d25\u7684 `shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu`\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u540e\u8005\u53ea\u662f\u590d\u7528\u540c\u4e00 PK expert \u96c6\u505a\u7b2c\u4e8c\u6b21 cleanup\uff0c\u800c\u8fd9\u91cc\u65b0\u589e\u7684\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u5168\u5c40 residual \u9759\u6001\u5e93\u3002\u4ee3\u7801\u5df2\u5b9e\u9645\u843d\u76d8\u5e76\u5b8c\u6210 exact-string smoke \u4e0e allowlist \u81ea\u68c0\uff1b\u5728\u5f53\u524d 2048 many-tiny recipe `K=32, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` \u4e0b\uff0c\u672c\u5730 exact \u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u4e3a selection_accesses=325696\u3001deployment_accesses=163840\u3001combined_accesses=489536\u3001exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625\uff0c\u4ecd\u5904\u4e8e `0.08~0.14` \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u5e76\u6ee1\u8db3\u786c\u9884\u7b97\u3002\u82e5\u60f3\u51fb\u8d25\u5f53\u524d incumbent r282 objective\u22480.268418\uff0c\u5219\u9700\u8981\u628a `exceed_alpha_0.50` \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 `0.151704` \u4ee5\u4e0b\u3002",
