research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4720:research/history/logs/agent_round_0298.stdout.log:575:research/history/logs/agent_action_0297.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r1(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r1(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res^τ(r2(x))} γ_m(x) c_m`，其中 `r1(x)=x-Σ_i α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh`，`r2(x)=r1(x)-Σ_{e,j} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`；`{b_i^sh}` 是 always-on shared 静态子库，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 PK 路由到的静态 expert 子库，`{c_m}` 是 tiny factorized residual 静态子库，最后一段系数 `γ_m(x)` 改为 JumpReLU-gated residual scorer。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时在线链路仍是“shared 查表 -> PK expert 子库查表 -> JumpReLU residual 子库查表 -> 加权求和 -> 选择性补偿”，不涉及动态字典生成，因此该 family 判定为 `扩展兼容`；不兼容 family 仍不得驱动当前 objective leaderboard。本轮唯一主假设是：当前 shared+PK scaffold 的主要缺口在 hard-token tail cleanup，而不是 shared bank 数量或 adaptive-active 轻微插值。相对 r282 只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`，保持 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, OPTIMIZER=adam, LR=8e-4` 与其余 recipe 不变，直接测试“把最终 tiny residual cleanup 从 plain factorized top-k 改成 thresholded JumpReLU residual”能否在近同成本下更强压低 `exceed_alpha_0.50`。本地精确成本自检显示该 family 在当前 recipe 下 `selection_accesses=325696`、`deployment_accesses=163840`、`combined_accesses=489536`、`exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`，满足预算；若想击败当前 incumbent `objective=0.2684179902076721`，需要把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到 `0.1517035126686096` 以下。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点以相同约 `0.1167x` 成本明显优于 r292 的 plain residual tail，并接近或击败 incumbent，则下一轮留在该 family，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，校准 shared coarse 与 JumpReLU tail cleanup 的预算分工。","如果该点优于 r292 但仍未赢 incumbent，则记录为“thresholded tail cleanup 比 plain residual 更适合当前 scaffold”，下一轮优先只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 向左探一格，尝试回收部分 cost 而保持 exceed 收益。","如果该点与 r292 持平或更差，则可更明确地下调 shared+PK 后接 tiny residual tail 这一整条邻域的优先级，后续应转向别的 scaffold-level cleanup 升级，而不是继续在 residual 语义上细扫。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际新增并注册 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`，真实落盘文件仅有 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`。","该 family 与 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的精确差异不是新增库或改 K，而是把最后一段 tiny factorized residual cleanup 的系数形成方式从 plain ReLU top-k 改成 JumpReLU-gated residual selection；shared coarse 与 PK expert cleanup 语义保持不变。","本地 exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual', k=32, expansion_factor=1, num_experts=2048, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56, stage1_ratio=0.25, factorized_hidden_dim=256)` 在 CUDA 上可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 override allowlist 校验已通过：对 `ARCHITECTURE/K/EXPANSION_FACTOR/NUM_EXPERTS/ACTIVE_EXPERTS/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT/STAGE1_RATIO/FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM/OPTIMIZER/LR` 的完整 recipe，`validate_env_overrides(...) == []`。","本地成本自检已通过：`selection_accesses=325696`、`deployment_accesses=163840`、`combined_accesses=489536`、`exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","当前 recipe 下 residual hidden dim 实际被 `min(latents_per_expert, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM)` 裁到 `56`，因此该新 family 的精确成本与现有 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 同档，适合做 matched cleanup-semantics probe。"],"reference_round":282,"self_review":"这轮满足代码类变更约束：我先真实落盘了新 family，再返回 `edit_sae_code`。修改范围保持最小，只做了 architecture whitelist、factory dispatch、具体类实现和 override allowlist，没有新增 tunable env key，也没有改 launcher / controller 语义。主假设也保持单一：只回答“thresholded tail cleanup 语义是否比 plain residual 更能压 low-K exceed”。主要风险是 JumpReLU 可能过度抑制 tiny residual bank，导致 tail 容量反而下降；如果结果如此，就应停止继续在这一条 residual-tail 语义上细扫。","summary":"已实现并注册 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`。建议本轮以 r282 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，做一轮 shared+PK scaffold 上的 matched cleanup-semantics probe，直接判断 JumpReLU tail residual 能否在约 `0.1167x` 成本下把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 明显压低。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4721:research/history/logs/agent_round_0298.stdout.log:663:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"NUM_EXPERTS","value":"3072"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r_sh(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`，其中 `{b_i^sh}` 是 always-on shared coarse 静态子库，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 product-key 路由到的静态 expert 子库；在线链路仍是“shared 查表 -> residual -> PK 选择少量静态 expert 子库 -> expert 内 JumpReLU sparse support -> 查表加权和 -> 选择性补偿”，不涉及动态字典生成，因此 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 仍判定为 `直接兼容`，不兼容 family 继续不得驱动当前 objective leaderboard。当前真正 blocker 不是工程接线，而是 round 297 的新 family `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual` 被 incubation limit policy 拦截，导致本轮不适合继续新开结构槽位；因此这轮应退回现有 winning scaffold，选择一个仍能回答高价值结构问题、且只改 1 个 env 的 matched probe。相对 r282 本轮只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=3072`，其余 `K=32, EF=1, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, OPTIMIZER=adam, LR=8e-4` 保持不变，直接测试 DeepSeekMoE 风格的“更细粒度 routed micro-experts”是否能在几乎不抬高 active path 和部署成本的前提下，把 hard-token exceed 再压低。这个改动不是继续扫 `K / STAGE1_RATIO / LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 的低信息近邻，而是在当前 best scaffold 上继续回答‘expert 分片粒度本身是不是当前 low-K exceed 的主瓶颈’。本地精确成本复核显示：`NUM_EXPERTS=3072` 时 `selection_accesses=285696`、`deployment_accesses=163840`、`combined_accesses=449536`、`exact total_cost_ratio=0.107177734375`，仍位于当前 `0.08~0.14` 主战场；若想击败 incumbent `objective=0.2684179902076721`，只需把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到 `0.1612402558326721` 以下。相比 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=64` 的 matched follow-up，这个 probe 成本更低且更贴近当前优先级最高的‘更细粒度 experts’结构问题。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点以仅约 `+0.0049x` 的 cost 增量把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到 `0.161` 左右并刷新 incumbent，则下一轮继续留在该 family，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=4096`，确认 many-tiny expert granularity 是否还在提供正交换率。","如果该点 exceed 有所下降但 objective 仍未赢过 r282，则记录为“更细粒度 micro-experts 有帮助，但交换率仍不够”，后续优先等待 incubation 槽位释放后回到真正的新 cleanup 语义，而不是继续在线性容量轴上多轮细扫。","如果该点与 r282 持平或更差，则可更明确地认定当前瓶颈不主要在 routed bank 粒度；后续即使有新预算，也应优先投向新的 cleanup/coarse 语义，而不是继续扩 `NUM_EXPERTS`。"],"notes_to_memory":["round 297 的 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual` 已成功落盘并注册，但被 policy 以 incubation limit=10 拦截，当前不能作为实际运行轮次推进。","本轮因此不再新开 family，而是回到现有 compatible winning scaffold `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，做一个单变量、高信息、偏向降 exceed 的 matched probe。","本地 smoke 已通过：`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 在 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=3072, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 下可 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 override allowlist 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'NUM_EXPERTS', value:'3072'}], fallback_architecture='shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu') == []`。","本地精确成本复核：`selection_accesses=285696`、`deployment_accesses=163840`、`combined_accesses=449536`、`exact total_cost_ratio=0.107177734375`；仍显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","对照成本表明：`NUM_EXPERTS=3072` 比 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=64` 更便宜（`0.10718x` vs `0.10815x`）且更直接回答‘更细粒度 routed micro-experts’这一当前高优先级问题，因此本轮优先选 `NUM_EXPERTS` 轴。"],"reference_round":282,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守单变量原则：相对 r282 只改 `NUM_EXPERTS`。我没有继续返回 `edit_sae_code`，因为 round 297 的代码改动已经真实落盘且本轮没有新增改动；同时，新 family 已被 incubation limit 拦截，继续开新结构会重复撞 policy。选择 `NUM_EXPERTS=3072` 而不是 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO` 的原因是：它仍属于现有 winning scaffold 上的容量组织问题，但比常规邻域细扫更接近当前 prompt 的 high-priority hypothesis，并且 exact cost 只小幅上升。主要风险是它仍然可能只是温和改善，不足以形成 regime shift；但在当前新 family 被 policy 阻塞的前提下，这是最干净、最可解释的 exceed-oriented probe。","summary":"建议本轮以 r282 为 reference，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=3072`。这是在不新开 family、且仅把 exact total_cost 从 `0.10229x` 提到 `0.10718x` 的前提下，对“更细粒度 micro-experts 是否能继续压低 low-K exceed”的直接 matched probe。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4722:research/history/logs/agent_action_0281.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 `x_hat = sum_{i in S_sh(x)} a_i^sh b_i^sh + sum_{e in E_pk(r1(x))} sum_{j in S_e^tau(r1(x))} beta_{e,j} c_{e,j} + sum_{e in E_pk(r1(x))} sum_{m in S_e^tau(r2(x))} gamma_{e,m} c_{e,m}`，其中 `r1(x)=x-shared(x)`，`r2(x)=r1(x)-cleanup1(x)`；shared coarse 子库 `{b_i^sh}` 与 routed expert 子库 `{c_{e,*}}` 都是静态向量库，第二次 cleanup 复用第一次 PK 选出的同一批静态 expert 子库，只是在更小 residual 上再做一次 expert-local JumpReLU 系数计算，因此在线导出仍是 LUTurbo/Lottable 可执行的“shared 查表 + PK 选子库 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判断为直接兼容。它与现有 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异不是换名字，而是在不增加 deployment K 的前提下，把 routed cleanup 从单次变成同一 expert set 上的两次 residual cleanup；它也不同于 `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，因为新增深度发生在 PK expert cleanup 内，而不是 shared bank 串联。相对 r266 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，保持 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=1024, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, adam, LR=8e-4` 不变，直接回答“在当前 winning scaffold 上，用更强 hard-token cleanup 语义而非更大 shared/coarse 或更轻 factorized head，能否以近同部署成本明显压低 exceed_alpha_0.50”。本地精确成本复核显示该新 family 的 `selection_accesses=352256, deployment_accesses=163840, combined_accesses=516096, exact total_cost_ratio=0.123046875`；要打赢 r266 的 exact objective≈0.275001，只需把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到约 `0.15195` 以下。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该 family 在约 0.123x 下把 exceed 明显压到 0.15 左右或更低，下一轮继续留在该 family，只做一次最小的 `STAGE1_RATIO` follow-up，确认 shared/coarse 与 stacked cleanup 的预算分配 knee。","如果该 family 只带来很小 exceed 改善，说明当前瓶颈不在“同一 expert set 的更深 cleanup”，后续应停止继续堆 PK cleanup 深度，转去别的 scaffold 升级槽位。","如果该 family 有清晰正信号但交换率仍不够，下一步更值得测试的是在该语义上叠加更厚 coarse scaffold，而不是回到 hash 或 factorized expert heads。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，修改文件为 `sparsify/config.py`, `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`, `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`, `research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md`。","exact-string smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu, K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=1024, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","override allowlist 本地校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key: ARCHITECTURE, value: shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu}], fallback_architecture='shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu')` 返回 `[]`。","本地精确成本对比：`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 为 `401408 / 0.095703125`，新 family 为 `516096 / 0.123046875`；新增成本只来自第二次 active expert encoder，deployment K 不变。","兼容性文档已补齐：`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 与新 family 现在都能从 `research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md` 解析为 `direct_compatible`。"],"reference_round":266,"self_review":"这轮满足当前阶段约束。主假设只有一个：在当前 best scaffold `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 上，不再扫 `K/LATENTS/STAGE1_RATIO` 邻域，而是引入一个真正不同的 cleanup 语义升级。工程改动控制在架构注册最小闭环内：config whitelist、factory dispatch、具体类实现、override allowlist、兼容性注册文档都已落盘；没有新增 tunable env key，因此未扩散到 `config_resolution/runner/scripts`。选择 r266 作为 reference 是因为它是当前 exact best scaffold；相对它只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，归因最干净。主要风险也很明确：新 family 虽把 cost 维持在现实的 0.123x 档位，但要赢过 r266 仍需把 exceed 从 0.179 附近压到约 0.152 以下，门槛不低；不过这比已有 0.19x shared-lowrank/two-stage 家族要求的 `exceed<0.09` 现实得多，也更贴近当前 prompt 的“更强 hard-token cleanup”问题。","summary":"已新增并本地验证 `shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。建议以 r266 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 做一轮 matched architecture probe，测试 shared coarse + PK routed cleanup 在复用同一 expert set 的两次 residual cleanup 后，是否能以 `exact total_cost_ratio=0.123046875` 显著压低 exceed_alpha_0.50。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4729:research/history/logs/agent_round_0301.stdout.log:2187:research/history/memory.json:3916:      "design_hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u8bbe\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(r1(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e^\u03c4(r1(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + \u03a3_{m\u2208S_res^\u03c4(r2(x))} \u03b3_m(x) c_m`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `r1(x)=x-\u03a3_i \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh`\uff0c`r2(x)=r1(x)-\u03a3_{e,j} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`\uff1b`{b_i^sh}` \u662f always-on shared coarse \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`{b_{e,j}}` \u662f product-key \u8def\u7531\u5230\u7684\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`{c_m}` \u662f tiny residual \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c\u800c\u6700\u540e\u4e00\u6bb5 residual \u7cfb\u6570 `\u03b3_m(x)` \u4f7f\u7528 JumpReLU-gated residual scorer\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u65f6\uff0c\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared \u67e5\u8868 -> PK expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 -> JumpReLU residual \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 -> \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`\u3001`product_key_expert_jumprelu`\u3001`dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u7b49\u517c\u5bb9 family \u4ecd\u53ef\u53c2\u4e0e\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9 family \u53ea\u80fd\u4f5c\u4e3a\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u540e\u7eed\u51b3\u7b56\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u5728\u8fde\u7eed\u4e24\u8f6e `NUM_EXPERTS` \u6269\u5bb9\u5df2\u663e\u793a 3072 \u6709\u9650\u6b63\u4fe1\u53f7\u30014096 \u660e\u663e\u56de\u64a4\u4e4b\u540e\uff0c\u5f53\u524d low-K \u4e3b\u74f6\u9888\u66f4\u50cf\u662f hard-token tail cleanup \u8bed\u4e4