\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u6269 routed bank \u7c92\u5ea6\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u5e94\u5207\u6362\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 incumbent family \u4e0a\u505a\u8fd1\u90bb\u63d2\u503c\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r282 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`\uff0c\u5176\u4f59 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=2048`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`\u3001`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4fdd\u6301\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u201c\u5728 winning shared+PK scaffold \u4e0a\uff0c\u628a\u6700\u7ec8 tiny residual cleanup \u4ece plain residual \u8bed\u4e49\u6362\u6210 JumpReLU-gated tail cleanup\u201d\u80fd\u5426\u66f4\u6709\u6548\u538b\u4f4e `exceed_alpha_0.50`\u3002\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u81ea\u68c0\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 `selection_accesses=325696`\u3001`deployment_accesses=163840`\u3001`combined_accesses=489536`\u3001`exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3\u9884\u7b97\uff1b\u82e5\u8981\u51fb\u8d25\u5f53\u524d incumbent `objective=0.2684179902076721`\uff0c\u9700\u8981\u628a `exceed_alpha_0.50` \u538b\u5230 `0.1517035126686096` \u4ee5\u4e0b\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4734:research/history/logs/agent_round_0301.stdout.log:2372:research/history/logs/agent_action_0293.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"扩展兼容新结构 probe：`shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual` 的最终重构为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk^*(r1(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r1(x))} α_{e,j} b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(r2(x))} γ_m c_m，其中 r1(x)=x-Σ α_i^sh b_i^sh，r2(x)=x-Σ α_i^sh b_i^sh-Σ α_{e,j} b_{e,j}。shared coarse、adaptive PK expert cleanup 与 residual cleanup 都落在静态向量库上，在线侧仍是 LUTurbo/Lottable 可导出的查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿流水线，因此兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设是：在 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的 cleanup scaffold 上加入 difficulty-aware adaptive-active expert path，能比固定 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 更强地降低 hard-token exceed，而 cost proxy 基本不变。","summary":"已实际新增并集成 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual`，只在 `sparsify/` 落盘修改 whitelist 与 runtime dispatch/class implementation。该 family 复用 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的 shared + PK + residual scaffold，仅把 expert cleanup 改成 adaptive-active 选择。按本地 smoke 与 cost 估计，在继承 r282 的 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 配置下 total_cost_ratio 仍约 `0.12x`，与 r288/r292 同量级；这使本轮成为一个纯粹检验“variable-active cleanup 是否能显著压低 exceed”的 matched-cost architecture probe。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这是一次有信息增量的新结构 probe，而不是继续扫已平台化的 split 邻域。风险在于 cost proxy 不会奖励 adaptive-active 的轻路径，所以若 exceed 改善不够，这条线可能仍输给 incumbent；但它正面回答了当前最高价值的问题：在保留 shared+PK+residual scaffold 的同时，difficulty-aware cleanup 是否值得继续。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["已落盘新增 family：`shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual`，并完成 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch/class 接线。","本地 exact-string smoke 已通过：`shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual` 在 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 下可实例化并 forward/backward。","本地 cost 估计：selection_ratio≈0.08，deployment_ratio≈0.04，total_cost_ratio≈0.12；与 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 同量级，适合作为 matched-cost exceed probe。","该 family 的结构语义是：shared coarse 吃主干，adaptive-active PK experts 按难度做 cleanup，最后 tiny residual head 做全局 tail cleanup；兼容性应视为扩展兼容。"],"next_hypotheses":["若本轮 exceed 明显低于 r288/r292 且 objective 接近或优于 incumbent，再以该 family 为 anchor 做一次最小 knee 校准，例如 `STAGE1_RATIO` 或 residual split。","若本轮 objective 仍无改善，则可将‘adaptive-active + residual cleanup’这条线一并降级，后续应转向真正不同的 coarse/shared 表达方式，而不是继续在 PK cleanup 语义上叠层。","若本轮出现 sanity 或 registration 异常，优先把它当新 family 集成问题处理，并用同一 exact architecture string 重做 smoke/dispatch 检查。"],"reference_round":282}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4735:research/history/logs/agent_round_0301.stdout.log:2373:research/history/round_summaries/round_0300.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u8bbe\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(r1(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e^\u03c4(r1(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + \u03a3_{m\u2208S_res^\u03c4(r2(x))} \u03b3_m(x) c_m`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `r1(x)=x-\u03a3_i \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh`\uff0c`r2(x)=r1(x)-\u03a3_{e,j} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`\uff1b`{b_i^sh}` \u662f always-on shared coarse \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`{b_{e,j}}` \u662f product-key \u8def\u7531\u5230\u7684\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`{c_m}` \u662f tiny residual \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c\u800c\u6700\u540e\u4e00\u6bb5 residual \u7cfb\u6570 `\u03b3_m(x)` \u4f7f\u7528 JumpReLU-gated residual scorer\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u65f6\uff0c\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared \u67e5\u8868 -> PK expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 -> JumpReLU residual \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 -> \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`\u3001`product_key_expert_jumprelu`\u3001`dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u7b49\u517c\u5bb9 family \u4ecd\u53ef\u53c2\u4e0e\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9 family \u53ea\u80fd\u4f5c\u4e3a\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u540e\u7eed\u51b3\u7b56\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u5728\u8fde\u7eed\u4e24\u8f6e `NUM_EXPERTS` \u6269\u5bb9\u5df2\u663e\u793a 3072 \u6709\u9650\u6b63\u4fe1\u53f7\u30014096 \u660e\u663e\u56de\u64a4\u4e4b\u540e\uff0c\u5f53\u524d low-K \u4e3b\u74f6\u9888\u66f4\u50cf\u662f hard-token tail cleanup \u8bed\u4e49\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u6269 routed bank \u7c92\u5ea6\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u5e94\u5207\u6362\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 incumbent family \u4e0a\u505a\u8fd1\u90bb\u63d2\u503c\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r282 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`\uff0c\u5176\u4f59 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=2048`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`\u3001`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4fdd\u6301\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u201c\u5728 winning shared+PK scaffold \u4e0a\uff0c\u628a\u6700\u7ec8 tiny residual cleanup \u4ece plain residual \u8bed\u4e49\u6362\u6210 JumpReLU-gated tail cleanup\u201d\u80fd\u5426\u66f4\u6709\u6548\u538b\u4f4e `exceed_alpha_0.50`\u3002\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u81ea\u68c0\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 `selection_accesses=325696`\u3001`deployment_accesses=163840`\u3001`combined_accesses=489536`\u3001`exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3\u9884\u7b97\uff1b\u82e5\u8981\u51fb\u8d25\u5f53\u524d incumbent `objective=0.2684179902076721`\uff0c\u9700\u8981\u628a `exceed_alpha_0.50` \u538b\u5230 `0.1517035126686096` \u4ee5\u4e0b\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4736:research/history/logs/agent_round_0301.stdout.log:2412:research/history/logs/agent_action_0300.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r1(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r1(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res^τ(r2(x))} γ_m(x) c_m`，其中 `r1(x)=x-Σ_i α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh`，`r2(x)=r1(x)-Σ_{e,j} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`；`{b_i^sh}` 是 always-on shared coarse 静态子库，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 product-key 路由到的静态 expert 子库，`{c_m}` 是 tiny residual 静态子库，而最后一段 residual 系数 `γ_m(x)` 使用 JumpReLU-gated residual scorer。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时，在线链路仍是“shared 查表 -> PK expert 子库查表 -> JumpReLU residual 子库查表 -> 有限加权和 -> 选择性在线补偿”，不涉及动态字典生成，因此该 family 判定为 `扩展兼容`。`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`、`product_key_expert_jumprelu`、`dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 等兼容 family 仍可参与当前 objective leaderboard；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 只能作为历史参考，不能驱动后续决策。本轮唯一主假设是：在连续两轮 `NUM_EXPERTS` 扩容已显示 3072 有限正信号、4096 明显回撤之后，当前 low-K 主瓶颈更像是 hard-token tail cleanup 语义，而不是继续扩 routed bank 粒度；因此应切换结构槽位，而不是继续在 incumbent family 上做近邻插值。相对 r282 只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`，其余 `K=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=2048`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 保持不变，直接测试“在 winning shared+PK scaffold 上，把最终 tiny residual cleanup 从 plain residual 语义换成 JumpReLU-gated tail cleanup”能否更有效压低 `exceed_alpha_0.50`。本地精确成本自检显示该点 `selection_accesses=325696`、`deployment_accesses=163840`、`combined_accesses=489536`、`exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`，满足预算；若要击败当前 incumbent `objective=0.2684179902076721`，需要把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到 `0.1517035126686096` 以下。","summary":"建议以 r282 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`。这轮不是继续做 incumbent 邻域扫参，而是在当前最强 shared+PK scaffold 上做一次 matched cleanup-semantics probe，直接判断 JumpReLU tail residual 能否在约 `0.1167x` 成本下把 exceed 明显压低。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮严格满足单变量原则：相对 r282 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。它也符合当前 round 300 的策略要求：最近两轮已经是同一 family 上的局部延伸且没有实质击穿 incumbent，因此本轮应优先换结构槽位，而不是继续做 `NUM_EXPERTS/K/STAGE1_RATIO` 近邻细扫。之所以选择这个 family，而不是再新开一个未注册 family，是因为它已经真实落盘、已完成 whitelist/factory/allowlist/smoke/cost 检查，并且当前本地 policy 校验已通过；r297 的失败只是当时全局 incubation 满额，而不是此 family 自身不可运行。主要风险是 JumpReLU 过度抑制 tiny residual bank，导致 tail cleanup 容量下降，结果不如 r292 的 plain residual；但这正是本轮要用一个最小结构切换清晰回答的问题。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual` 已在更早轮次真实落盘并完成注册，实际修改文件是 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`；本轮无需再做代码编辑。","该 family 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是静态 shared 子库 + 静态 PK expert 子库 + 静态 residual 子库上的有限加权和，兼容性标签应记为 `扩展兼容`。","本地 exact-string smoke、override allowlist 和成本自检都已通过；当前 recipe 下 `exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`。","r297 被 `policy_reject` 的原因仅是当时新 family 进入 incubating 时撞上 incubation 上限，不是 wiring 或兼容性错误；当前用本地 `validate_action(...)` 对同一 `ARCHITECTURE` param_only 提案复核已通过。","r298 与 r299 共同说明 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 上继续扩 `NUM_EXPERTS` 已接近 knee：3072 有限正信号，但 4096 已明显回撤，因此当前更该测试 cleanup 语义升级。","若本轮结果仍不能优于 r292 的 same-cost plain residual 版本，则 shared+PK 后接 tiny residual cleanup 这整条邻域应整体降级，不再继续细扫 residual 语义。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 `0.1167x` 成本下明显优于 r292，并接近或击败 incumbent，则下一轮留在该 family，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，校准 shared coarse 与 JumpReLU tail cleanup 的预算分工。","如果该点优于 r292 但仍未赢 incumbent，则说明 cleanup 语义升级方向成立但交换率仍不足；下一轮优先只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 向左探一格，尝试回收部分 cost 而保留 exceed 收益。","如果该点与 r292 持平或更差，则说明当前瓶颈不在 residual gating 语义；后续应停止沿 shared+PK+tiny-residual 邻域继续细扫，转向别的 scaffold-level cleanup 或 coarse 表达升级。"],"reference_round":282}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4737:research/history/logs/agent_round_0301.stdout.log:2433:research/history/round_summaries/round_0293.json:20:    "summary": "\u5df2\u5b9e\u9645\u65b0\u589e\u5e76\u96c6\u6210 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual`\uff0c\u53ea\u5728 `sparsify/` \u843d\u76d8\u4fee\u6539 whitelist \u4e0e runtime dispatch/class implementation\u3002\u8be5 family \u590d\u7528 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` \u7684 shared + PK + residual scaffold\uff0c\u4ec5\u628a expert cleanup \u6539\u6210 adaptive-active \u9009\u62e9\u3002\u6309\u672c\u5730 smoke \u4e0e cost \u4f30\u8ba1\uff0c\u5728\u7ee7\u627f r282 \u7684 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` \u914d\u7f6e\u4e0b total_cost_ratio \u4ecd\u7ea6 `0.12x`\uff0c\u4e0e r288/r292 \u540c\u91cf\u7ea7\uff1b\u8fd9\u4f7f\u672c\u8f6e\u6210\u4e3a\u4e00\u4e2a\u7eaf\u7cb9\u68c0\u9a8c\u201cvariable-active cleanup \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u663e\u8457\u538b\u4f4e exceed\u201d\u7684 matched-cost architecture probe\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4738:research/history/logs/agent_round_0301.stdout.log:2436:research/history/round_summaries/round_0293.json:73:    "description": "\u5df2\u5b9e\u9645\u65b0\u589e\u5e76\u96c6\u6210 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual`\uff0c\u53ea\u5728 `sparsify/` \u843d\u76d8\u4fee\u6539 whitelist \u4e0e runtime dispatch/class implementation\u3002\u8be5 family \u590d\u7528 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` \u7684 shared + PK + residual scaffold\uff0c\u4ec5\u628a expert cleanup \u6539\u6210 adaptive-active \u9009\u62e9\u3002\u6309\u672c\u5730 smoke \u4e0e cost \u4f30\u8ba1\uff0c\u5728\u7ee7\u627f r282 \u7684 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` \u914d\u7f6e\u4e0b total_cost_ratio \u4ecd\u7ea6 `0.12x`\uff0c\u4e0e r288/r292 \u540c\u91cf\u7ea7\uff1b\u8fd9\u4f7f\u672c\u8f6e\u6210\u4e3a\u4e00\u4e2a\u7eaf\u7cb9\u68c0\u9a8c\u201cvariable-active cleanup \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u663e\u8457\u538b\u4f4e exceed\u201d\u7684 matched-cost architecture probe\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4739:research/history/logs/agent_round_0301.stdout.log:2484:research/history/logs/agent_action_0297.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r1(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r1(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res^τ(r2(x))} γ_m(x) c_m`，其中 `r1(x)=x-Σ_i α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh`，`r2(x)=r1(x)-Σ_{e,j} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`；`{b_i^sh}` 是 always-on shared 静态子库，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 PK 路由到的静态 expert 子库，`{c_m}` 是 tiny factorized residual 静态子库，最后一段系数 `γ_m(x)` 改为 JumpReLU-gated residual scorer。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时在线链路仍是“shared 查表 -> PK expert 子库查表 -> JumpReLU residual 子库查表 -> 加权求和 -> 选择性补偿”，不涉及动态字典生成，因此该 family 判定为 `扩展兼容`；不兼容 family 仍不得驱动当前 objective leaderboard。本轮唯一主假设是：当前 shared+PK scaffold 的主要缺口在 hard-token tail cleanup，而不是 shared bank 数量或 adaptive-active 轻微插值。相对 r282 只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`，保持 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, OPTIMIZER=adam, LR=8e-4` 与其余 recipe 不变，直接测试“把最终 tiny residual cleanup 从 plain factorized top-k 改成 thresholded JumpReLU residual”能否在近同成本下更强压低 `exceed_alpha_0.50`。本地精确成本自检显示该 family 在当前 recipe 下 `selection_accesses=325696`、`deployment_accesses=163840`、`combined_accesses=489536`、`exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`，满足预算；若想击败当前 incumbent `objective=0.2684179902076721`，需要把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到 `0.1517035126686096` 以下。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点以相同约 `0.1167x` 成本明显优于 r292 的 plain residual tail，并接近或击败 incumbent，则下一轮留在该 family，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，校准 shared coarse 与 JumpReLU tail cleanup 的预算分工。","如果该点优于 r292 但仍未赢 incumbent，则记录为“thresholded tail cleanup 比 plain residual 更适合当前 scaffold”，下一轮优先只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 向左探一格，尝试回收部分 cost 而保持 exceed 收益。","如果该点与 r292 持平或更差，则可更明确地下调 shared+PK 后接 tiny residual tail 这一整条邻域的优先级，后续应转向别的 scaffold-level cleanup 升级，而不是继续在 residual 语义上细扫。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际新增并注册 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`，真实落盘文件仅有 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`。","该 family 与 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的精确差异不是新增库或改 K，而是把最后一段 tiny factorized residual cleanup 的系数形成方式从 plain ReLU top-k 改成 JumpReLU-gated residual selection；shared coarse 与 PK expert cleanup 语义保持不变。","本地 exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual', k=32, expansion_factor=1, num_experts=2048, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56, stage1_ratio=0.25, factorized_hidden_dim=256)` 在 CUDA 上可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 override allowlist 校验已通过：对 `ARCHITECTURE/K/EXPANSION_FACTOR/NUM_EXPERTS/ACTIVE_EXPERTS/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT/STAGE1_RATIO/FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM/OPTIMIZER/LR` 的完整 recipe，`validate_env_overrides(...) == []`。","本地成本自检已通过：`selection_accesses=325696`、`deployment_accesses=163840`、`combined_accesses=489536`、`exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","当前 recipe 下 residual hidden dim 实际被 `min(latents_per_expert, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM)` 裁到 `56`，因此该新 family 的精确成本与现有 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 同档，适合做 matched cleanup-semantics probe。"],"reference_round":282,"self_review":"这轮满足代码类变更约束：我先真实落盘了新 family，再返回 `edit_sae_code`。修改范围保持最小，只做了 architecture whitelist、factory dispatch、具体类实现和 override allowlist，没有新增 tunable env key，也没有改 launcher / controller 语义。主假设也保持单一：只回答“thresholded tail cleanup 语义是否比 plain residual 更能压 low-K exceed”。主要风险是 JumpReLU 可能过度抑制 tiny residual bank，导致 tail 容量反而下降；如果结果如此，就应停止继续在这一条 residual-tail 语义上细扫。","summary":"已实现并注册 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`。建议本轮以 r282 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，做一轮 shared+PK scaffold 上的 matched cleanup-semantics probe，直接判断 JumpReLU tail residual 能否在约 `0.1167x` 成本下把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 明显压低。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4740:research/history/logs/agent_round_0301.stdout.log:2553:research/history/logs/agent_action_0284.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 `x_hat = Σ_{s=1..2} Σ_{i∈S_s(x)} α_{s,i}^sh(x) b_{s,i}^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r_sh(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`，其中两个 always-on shared coarse 静态子库 `{b_{s,i}^sh}` 先吸收更厚的公共主干，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 product-key 路由到的静态 expert 子库，在线推理仍可直接导出为 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“多 shared 查表 + PK 选少量静态 expert 子库 + expert 内 JumpReLU sparse support + 查表加权和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，不涉及动态字典生成，因此兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 r282，本轮只改 `ARCHITECTURE=dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，保持 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与训练配方不变，直接回答在已经被 r282 证明有效的 finer-grained micro-expert scaffold 上，更厚的 shared coarse 主干是否能在近同成本下进一步压低 hard-token exceed。它与已失败的 r283 adaptive-active probe 不同，变化不在 active-path，而在 coarse/shared 表达能力；这正对应当前 prompt 更高优先级的“建立在 winning scaffold 上的 shared/coarse 表达升级”。本地成本复核显示该 family 在 r282 同 recipe 下 `selection_accesses=322560`、`deployment_accesses=163840`、`combined_accesses=486400`、`exact total_cost_ratio=0.115966796875`，仍位于当前 `0.08~0.14` 主战场内。要打赢 r282 的 exact objective≈0.268418，需要把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到约 `0.152451` 以下。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该 family 在约 0.116x 下把 exceed 明显压到 0.152 附近或更低，说明当前更有价值的升级方向是 thicker shared coarse scaffold，而不是继续扩 bank 或继续做 variable-active path；下一轮只做一次最小的 shared/expert 预算校准。","如果该 family 只带来很小 exceed 改善或 objective 仍不如 r282，说明双 shared coarse 在当前 many-tiny scaffold 上交换率仍不够；后续应停止继续堆 shared banks，转去别的结构槽位。","如果结果介于 r279 与 r282 之间，应把结论记录为‘更厚 coarse 有帮助但不够形成 regime shift’，之后更值得探索的是新的 cleanup 语义或 shared low-rank trunk，而不是继续 dual-shared 邻域细扫。"],"notes_to_memory":["r282 已证明在 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 上把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 提到 2048 能把 objective 拉到当前 best 0.268418，说明 finer-grained micro-expert 容量是真实正信号。","r283 的负信号说明在该新 scaffold 上，variable-active 1-or-2 expert path 仍没有换回更低 exceed，因此 adaptive-active 方向在当前 hookpoint 上应暂时下调优先级。","本轮选择的是建立在 r282 scaffold 上的 matched architecture probe，而不是继续扫 `NUM_EXPERTS` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO` 邻点。","本地精确成本复核：`dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu K=32 NUM_EXPERTS=2048 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 的 `combined_accesses=486400`、`exact total_cost_ratio=0.115966796875`，仍满足预算。"],"reference_round":282,"self_review":"这轮满足单变量原则：相对 r282 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。之所以不继续在 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 上把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 从 2048 线性扩到 3072/4096，是因为 r282 已经给出 recent 改进，而 r283 又说明并非所有基于该 scaffold 的轻量 follow-up 都有效；按当前阶段规则，更有价值的是回答哪个结构升级值得继续，而不是让同 family 容量插值重新主导预算。之所以不选 `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 或 `shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，是因为它们最近已给出更弱或近似持平的信号；`dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 则是当前最干净、最贴近 prompt 中‘shared/coarse 表达升级’的 matched probe。主要风险是 exact cost 升到约 0.116x 后，需要 exceed 比 r282 再降约 0.016 才能赢；如果做不到，就能更明确地结束 dual-shared 这条 coarse-thickening 支线。","summary":"建议以 r282 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，在 `NUM_EXPERTS=2048` 的 finer-grained micro-expert scaffold 上做一轮 matched architecture probe，直接测试更厚 shared coarse 主干能否把 exceed_alpha_0.50 压到足以刷新当前 best objective。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4741:research/history/logs/agent_round_0301.stdout.log:2570:research/history/logs/agent_action_0288.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r_1(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_1(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(r_2(x))} γ_m(x) c_m`，其中 `r_1(x)=x-Σ_i α_i^sh b_i^sh`，`r_2(x)=r_1(x)-Σ_{e,j} α_{e,j} b_{e,j}`。第一项是 always-on shared coarse 静态子库，第二项是在残差上由 product-key 选出的少量静态 expert 子库内的 JumpReLU cleanup，第三项是一个很小的 factorized global residual 静态库做 tail cleanup；在线链路仍是“shared 查表 -> residual -> PK expert 子库查表 -> residual -> tiny factorized residual 子库查表 -> 有限加权和”，不依赖动态字典，因此新 family `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 判定为扩展兼容。明确不兼容 family 仍只作历史参考，不得驱动当前兼容 leaderboard。本轮唯一主假设是：r283-r287 已基本否定现有 `shared+PK` 邻域里的 adaptive-active、dual-shared、residual-shared、shared-lowrank 与 plain-PK control，但这些失败主要说明旧 cleanup 语义没有形成 regime shift；当前更高信息量的问题是，在保留 winning scaffold `shared coarse + PK routed cleanup` 的前提下，额外加一个很小的全局 residual tail-cleanup 库，能否把 hard-token exceed 再压下去。新 family 相对现有 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异不是重命名，而是在 shared coarse 与 PK cleanup 之后新增一个 tiny factorized residual bank；它也不同于已失败的 `shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，因为后者只是复用同一 PK expert 集做第二次 cleanup，而这里新增的是一个全局 residual 静态库。代码已实际落盘并完成 exact-string smoke 与 allowlist 自检；在当前 2048 many-tiny recipe `K=32, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 下，本地 exact 成本复核为 selection_accesses=325696、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=489536、exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625，仍处于 `0.08~0.14` 主战场并满足硬预算。若想击败当前 incumbent r282 objective≈0.268418，则需要把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到约 `0.151704` 以下。","summary":"已新增并接通 `shared_product_key_expert_residual`。建议以 r282 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_residual`，在同一 2048 many-tiny scaffold 上做一轮新的 matched architecture probe，直接测试“shared coarse + PK routed cleanup + tiny global residual tail-cleanup”是否能在约 `0.1167x` 成本下更强地降低 exceed。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_product_key_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮符合当前策略约束。最近 5 轮都没有把 objective 拉过 r282，继续在已有 `shared+PK` 邻域做 `K/STAGE1_RATIO/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 近邻细扫已经明显低信息；而 plain PK、shared-lowrank、dual-shared、residual-dual-shared、shared adaptive-active 都给了更新且更直接的负信号。与其在这些已知弱槽位里继续补点，更有价值的是新开一个建立在 winning scaffold 之上的 cleanup 语义升级。代码改动限制在最小必要文件：`sparsify/config.py` whitelist、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch+实现、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py` allowlist、`research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md` compatibility 行；没有新增 tunable env key，因此不需要改 `controller.py`、`config_resolution.py` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。主要风险是新加的 tiny residual bank 会抬高 encoder cost，却换不回足够多的 exceed 改善；但这正是当前单目标下最值得一次性回答的结构问题，而且 exact cost 仍稳在可接受带内。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_product_key_expert_residual"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `shared_product_key_expert_residual`，真实改动文件为 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`、`research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md`。","该 family 的精确结构语义是：保留 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的 shared coarse + PK expert cleanup，再追加一个 tiny factorized global residual cleanup；它不是 `shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 或 `shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的重命名。","exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='shared_product_key_expert_residual', k=32, expansion_factor=1, num_experts=2048, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56, stage1_ratio=0.25, factorized_hidden_dim=256)` 可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 override allowlist 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'ARCHITECTURE', value:'shared_product_key_expert_residual'}], fallback_architecture='shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu')` 返回 `[]`。","本地 exact 成本复核：selection_accesses=325696、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=489536、exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625；在当前 fused-QKV proxy 下满足硬预算。","兼容性表已补充该 family：`shared_product_key_expert_residual` 应按扩展兼容处理；当前 objective leaderboard 仍只比较兼容 family。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果该 family 在约 `0.1167x` 下显著降低 exceed 并击败 r282，则下一轮继续留在该 family，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，优先测试 shared coarse 与 tail-cleanup 的预算分配 knee。","如果该 family 只比 r284/r287 之类 shared-ordering 变体更好、但仍输给 r282，则说明新的全局 residual cleanup 语义有一定价值但不够形成 regime shift；后续可只保留一轮必要校准，否则应继续切换结构槽位。","如果该 family 与 r282 基本持平或更差，则可更明确地记录：当前 hookpoint 上额外的 tiny global residual bank 也不足以修复 low-K tail，之后应下调这类“shared+PK 后接轻 residual”方向的优先级。"],"reference_round":282}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4744:research/history/logs/agent_round_0301.stdout.log:2678:research/history/round_summaries/round_0298.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(r_sh(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e^\u03c4(r_sh(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `{b_i^sh}` \u662f always-on shared coarse \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`{b_{e,j}}` \u662f product-key \u8def\u7531\u5230\u7684\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared \u67e5\u8868 -> residual -> PK \u9009\u62e9\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> expert \u5185 JumpReLU sparse support -> \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u4ecd\u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9`\uff0c\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9 family \u7ee7\u7eed\u4e0d\u5f97\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u5f53\u524d\u771f\u6b63 blocker \u4e0d\u662f\u5de5\u7a0b\u63a5\u7ebf\uff0c\u800c\u662f round 297 \u7684\u65b0 family `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual` \u88ab incubation limit policy \u62e6\u622a\uff0c\u5bfc\u81f4\u672c\u8f6e\u4e0d\u9002\u5408\u7ee7\u7eed\u65b0\u5f00\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u8fd9\u8f6e\u5e94\u9000\u56de\u73b0\u6709 winning scaffold\uff0c\u9009\u62e9\u4e00\u4e2a\u4ecd\u80fd\u56de\u7b54\u9ad8\u4ef7\u503c\u7ed3\u6784\u95ee\u9898\u3001\u4e14\u53ea\u6539 1 \u4e2a env \u7684 matched probe\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r282 \u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u6539 `NUM_EXPERTS=3072`\uff0c\u5176\u4f59 `K=32, EF=1, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, OPTIMIZER=adam, LR=8e-4` \u4fdd\u6301\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5 DeepSeekMoE \u98ce\u683c\u7684\u201c\u66f4\u7ec6\u7c92\u5ea6 routed micro-experts\u201d\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5728\u51e0\u4e4e\u4e0d\u62ac\u9ad8 active path \u548c\u90e8\u7f72\u6210\u672c\u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u628a hard-token exceed \u518d\u538b\u4f4e\u3002\u8fd9\u4e2a\u6539\u52a8\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u626b `K / STAGE1_RATIO / LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` \u7684\u4f4e\u4fe1\u606f\u8fd1\u90bb\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u5728\u5f53\u524d best scaffold \u4e0a\u7ee7\u7eed\u56de\u7b54\u2018expert \u5206\u7247\u7c92\u5ea6\u672c\u8eab\u662f\u4e0d\u662f\u5f53\u524d low-K exceed \u7684\u4e3b\u74f6\u9888\u2019\u3002\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\uff1a`NUM_EXPERTS=3072` \u65f6 `selection_accesses=285696`\u3001`deployment_accesses=163840`\u3001`combined_accesses=449536`\u3001`exact total_cost_ratio=0.107177734375`\uff0c\u4ecd\u4f4d\u4e8e\u5f53\u524d `0.08~0.14` \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\uff1b\u82e5\u60f3\u51fb\u8d25 incumbent `objective=0.2684179902076721`\uff0c\u53ea\u9700\u628a `exceed_alpha_0.50` \u538b\u5230 `0.1612402558326721` \u4ee5\u4e0b\u3002\u76f8\u6bd4 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=64` \u7684 matched follow-up\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e2a probe \u6210\u672c\u66f4\u4f4e\u4e14\u66f4\u8d34\u8fd1\u5f53\u524d\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u6700\u9ad8\u7684\u2018\u66f4\u7ec6\u7c92\u5ea6 experts\u2019\u7ed3\u6784\u95ee\u9898\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:4745:research/history/logs/agent_round_0301.stdout.log:2893:research/history/round_summaries/round_0297.json:18:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u8bbe\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(r1(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e^\u03c4(r1(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + \u03a3_{m\u2208S_res^\u03c4(r2(x))} \u03b3_m(x) c_m`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `r1(x)=x-\u03a3_i \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh`\uff0c`r2(x)=r1(x)-\u03a3_{e,j} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`\uff1b`{b_i^sh}` \u662f always-on shared \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`{b_{e,j}}` \u662f PK \u8def\u7531\u5230\u7684\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`{c_m}` \u662f tiny factorized residual \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c\u6700\u540e\u4e00\u6bb5\u7cfb\u6570 `\u03b3_m(x)` \u6539\u4e3a JumpReLU-gated residual scorer\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u65f6\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared \u67e5\u8868 -> PK expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 -> JumpReLU residual \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 -> \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\uff1b\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9 family \u4ecd\u4e0d\u5f97\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u5f53\u524d shared+PK scaffold \u7684\u4e3b\u8981\u7f3a\u53e3\u5728 hard-token tail cleanup\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f shared bank \u6570\u91cf\u6216 adaptive-active \u8f7b\u5fae\u63d2\u503c\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r282 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, OPTIMIZER=adam, LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59 recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u201c\u628a\u6700\u7ec8 tiny residual cleanup \u4ece plain factorized top-k \u6539\u6210 thresholded JumpReLU residual\u201d\u80fd\u5426\u5728\u8fd1\u540c\u6210\u672c\u4e0b\u66f4\u5f3a\u538b\u4f4e `exceed_alpha_0.50`\u3002\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u81ea\u68c0\u663e\u793a\u8be5 family \u5728\u5f53\u524d recipe \u4e0b `selection_accesses=325696`\u3001`deployment_accesses=163840`\u3001`combined_accesses=489536`\u3001`exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3\u9884\u7b97\uff1b\u82e5\u60f3\u51fb\u8d25\u5f53\u524d incumbent `objective=0.2684179902076721`\uff0c\u9700\u8981\u628a `exceed_alpha_0.50` \u538b\u5230 `0.1517035126686096` \u4ee5\u4e0b\u3002",
