research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:5029:research/history/logs/agent_round_0303.stdout.log:1318:research/history/results.tsv:282:r281_1775051537	1775051537	ok	archive	0.16358110308647156	0.180772	0.303819	516096.000000	0.123047	352256.000000	0.083984	163840.000000	0.039062	32	shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu	1				/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0281/round0281_standard_1775050717_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef1_k32_20260401_213844	6681cb1731695f2cb2ebe91a0adb9898def82b4b			已新增并本地验证 `shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。建议以 r266 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 做一轮 matched architecture probe，测试 shared coarse + PK routed cleanup 在复用同一 expert set 的两次 residual cleanup 后，是否能以 `exact total_cost_ratio=0.123046875` 显著压低 exceed_alpha_0.50。	这轮满足当前阶段约束。主假设只有一个：在当前 best scaffold `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 上，不再扫 `K/LATENTS/STAGE1_RATIO` 邻域，而是引入一个真正不同的 cleanup 语义升级。工程改动控制在架构注册最小闭环内：config whitelist、factory dispatch、具体类实现、override allowlist、兼容性注册文档都已落盘；没有新增 tunable env key，因此未扩散到 `config_resolution/runner/scripts`。选择 r266 作为 reference 是因为它是当前 exact best scaffold；相对它只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，归因最干净。主要风险也很明确：新 family 虽把 cost 维持在现实的 0.123x 档位，但要赢过 r266 仍需把 exceed 从 0.179 附近压到约 0.152 以下，门槛不低；不过这比已有 0.19x shared-lowrank/two-stage 家族要求的 `exceed<0.09` 现实得多，也更贴近当前 prompt 的“更强 hard-token cleanup”问题。	/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/round0281_standard_1775050717.log
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:5031:research/history/logs/agent_round_0303.stdout.log:1321:research/history/results.tsv:294:r293_1775063569	1775063569	ok	archive	0.1473383903503418	0.164479	0.281193	489536.000000	0.116714	325696.000000	0.077652	163840.000000	0.039062	32	shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual	1				/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0293/round0293_standard_1775062748_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef1_k32_20260402_005914	234e846f7a8fb76971dd8d179f9901aec8eb844a			已实际新增并集成 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual`，只在 `sparsify/` 落盘修改 whitelist 与 runtime dispatch/class implementation。该 family 复用 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的 shared + PK + residual scaffold，仅把 expert cleanup 改成 adaptive-active 选择。按本地 smoke 与 cost 估计，在继承 r282 的 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 配置下 total_cost_ratio 仍约 `0.12x`，与 r288/r292 同量级；这使本轮成为一个纯粹检验“variable-active cleanup 是否能显著压低 exceed”的 matched-cost architecture probe。	这是一次有信息增量的新结构 probe，而不是继续扫已平台化的 split 邻域。风险在于 cost proxy 不会奖励 adaptive-active 的轻路径，所以若 exceed 改善不够，这条线可能仍输给 incumbent；但它正面回答了当前最高价值的问题：在保留 shared+PK+residual scaffold 的同时，difficulty-aware cleanup 是否值得继续。	/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/round0293_standard_1775062748.log
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:5032:research/history/logs/agent_round_0303.stdout.log:1327:research/history/round_summaries/round_0288.json:20:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u8bbe\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(r_1(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e^\u03c4(r_1(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + \u03a3_{m\u2208S_res(r_2(x))} \u03b3_m(x) c_m`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `r_1(x)=x-\u03a3_i \u03b1_i^sh b_i^sh`\uff0c`r_2(x)=r_1(x)-\u03a3_{e,j} \u03b1_{e,j} b_{e,j}`\u3002\u7b2c\u4e00\u9879\u662f always-on shared coarse \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c\u7b2c\u4e8c\u9879\u662f\u5728\u6b8b\u5dee\u4e0a\u7531 product-key \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u5185\u7684 JumpReLU cleanup\uff0c\u7b2c\u4e09\u9879\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u5f88\u5c0f\u7684 factorized global residual \u9759\u6001\u5e93\u505a tail cleanup\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared \u67e5\u8868 -> residual -> PK expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 -> residual -> tiny factorized residual \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 -> \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u4f9d\u8d56\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u65b0 family `shared_product_key_expert_residual` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u660e\u786e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9 family \u4ecd\u53ea\u4f5c\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u5f97\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d\u517c\u5bb9 leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1ar283-r287 \u5df2\u57fa\u672c\u5426\u5b9a\u73b0\u6709 `shared+PK` \u90bb\u57df\u91cc\u7684 adaptive-active\u3001dual-shared\u3001residual-shared\u3001shared-lowrank \u4e0e plain-PK control\uff0c\u4f46\u8fd9\u4e9b\u5931\u8d25\u4e3b\u8981\u8bf4\u660e\u65e7 cleanup \u8bed\u4e49\u6ca1\u6709\u5f62\u6210 regime shift\uff1b\u5f53\u524d\u66f4\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u662f\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u7559 winning scaffold `shared coarse + PK routed cleanup` \u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u989d\u5916\u52a0\u4e00\u4e2a\u5f88\u5c0f\u7684\u5168\u5c40 residual tail-cleanup \u5e93\uff0c\u80fd\u5426\u628a hard-token exceed \u518d\u538b\u4e0b\u53bb\u3002\u65b0 family \u76f8\u5bf9\u73b0\u6709 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u7684\u7cbe\u786e\u5dee\u5f02\u4e0d\u662f\u91cd\u547d\u540d\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u5728 shared coarse \u4e0e PK cleanup \u4e4b\u540e\u65b0\u589e\u4e00\u4e2a tiny factorized residual bank\uff1b\u5b83\u4e5f\u4e0d\u540c\u4e8e\u5df2\u5931\u8d25\u7684 `shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu`\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u540e\u8005\u53ea\u662f\u590d\u7528\u540c\u4e00 PK expert \u96c6\u505a\u7b2c\u4e8c\u6b21 cleanup\uff0c\u800c\u8fd9\u91cc\u65b0\u589e\u7684\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u5168\u5c40 residual \u9759\u6001\u5e93\u3002\u4ee3\u7801\u5df2\u5b9e\u9645\u843d\u76d8\u5e76\u5b8c\u6210 exact-string smoke \u4e0e allowlist \u81ea\u68c0\uff1b\u5728\u5f53\u524d 2048 many-tiny recipe `K=32, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` \u4e0b\uff0c\u672c\u5730 exact \u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u4e3a selection_accesses=325696\u3001deployment_accesses=163840\u3001combined_accesses=489536\u3001exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625\uff0c\u4ecd\u5904\u4e8e `0.08~0.14` \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u5e76\u6ee1\u8db3\u786c\u9884\u7b97\u3002\u82e5\u60f3\u51fb\u8d25\u5f53\u524d incumbent r282 objective\u22480.268418\uff0c\u5219\u9700\u8981\u628a `exceed_alpha_0.50` \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 `0.151704` \u4ee5\u4e0b\u3002",
