research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:5194:research/history/logs/agent_round_0297.stdout.log:1659:research/history/results.tsv:282:r281_1775051537	1775051537	ok	archive	0.16358110308647156	0.180772	0.303819	516096.000000	0.123047	352256.000000	0.083984	163840.000000	0.039062	32	shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu	1				/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0281/round0281_standard_1775050717_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef1_k32_20260401_213844	6681cb1731695f2cb2ebe91a0adb9898def82b4b			已新增并本地验证 `shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。建议以 r266 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 做一轮 matched architecture probe，测试 shared coarse + PK routed cleanup 在复用同一 expert set 的两次 residual cleanup 后，是否能以 `exact total_cost_ratio=0.123046875` 显著压低 exceed_alpha_0.50。	这轮满足当前阶段约束。主假设只有一个：在当前 best scaffold `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 上，不再扫 `K/LATENTS/STAGE1_RATIO` 邻域，而是引入一个真正不同的 cleanup 语义升级。工程改动控制在架构注册最小闭环内：config whitelist、factory dispatch、具体类实现、override allowlist、兼容性注册文档都已落盘；没有新增 tunable env key，因此未扩散到 `config_resolution/runner/scripts`。选择 r266 作为 reference 是因为它是当前 exact best scaffold；相对它只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，归因最干净。主要风险也很明确：新 family 虽把 cost 维持在现实的 0.123x 档位，但要赢过 r266 仍需把 exceed 从 0.179 附近压到约 0.152 以下，门槛不低；不过这比已有 0.19x shared-lowrank/two-stage 家族要求的 `exceed<0.09` 现实得多，也更贴近当前 prompt 的“更强 hard-token cleanup”问题。	/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/round0281_standard_1775050717.log
research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:5196:research/history/logs/agent_round_0297.stdout.log:1668:research/history/results.tsv:294:r293_1775063569	1775063569	ok	archive	0.1473383903503418	0.164479	0.281193	489536.000000	0.116714	325696.000000	0.077652	163840.000000	0.039062	32	shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual	1				/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0293/round0293_standard_1775062748_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef1_k32_20260402_005914	234e846f7a8fb76971dd8d179f9901aec8eb844a			已实际新增并集成 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual`，只在 `sparsify/` 落盘修改 whitelist 与 runtime dispatch/class implementation。该 family 复用 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的 shared + PK + residual scaffold，仅把 expert cleanup 改成 adaptive-active 选择。按本地 smoke 与 cost 估计，在继承 r282 的 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 配置下 total_cost_ratio 仍约 `0.12x`，与 r288/r292 同量级；这使本轮成为一个纯粹检验“variable-active cleanup 是否能显著压低 exceed”的 matched-cost architecture probe。	这是一次有信息增量的新结构 probe，而不是继续扫已平台化的 split 邻域。风险在于 cost proxy 不会奖励 adaptive-active 的轻路径，所以若 exceed 改善不够，这条线可能仍输给 incumbent；但它正面回答了当前最高价值的问题：在保留 shared+PK+residual scaffold 的同时，difficulty-aware cleanup 是否值得继续。	/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/round0293_standard_1775062748.log
