research/history/logs/agent_round_0304.stdout.log:5968:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_cascade_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_cascade_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh b_i^sh + Σ_{j∈S_{e1(r1)}^τ(r1)} β_j c_{e1,j} + Σ_{m∈S_{e2(r1)}^τ(r2)} γ_m c_{e2,m}`，其中 `r1(x)=x-shared(x)`，`r2(x)=r1(x)-expert1_cleanup(r1)`，而 `(e1,e2)` 是同一次 product-key 路由在 `r1` 上选出的有序 top-2 静态 expert 子库。在线侧仍可导出为“shared 静态库查表 + PK 选择静态 expert 子库 + 有限加权和 + 选择性补偿”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此兼容性判断为 `直接兼容`。相对 r282，本轮只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 改为 `shared_cascade_product_key_expert_jumprelu`；主假设是：在保持几乎相同 proxy cost 的前提下，把 flat top-2 expert cleanup 改成 ordered coarse-to-fine residual cascade，会比现有 winning scaffold 更直接压低 hard-token tail error，从而降低 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 并刷新 objective。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该 family 在同成本下把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到约 `0.166` 或更低并赢下 r282，则下一轮只改 `STAGE1_RATIO` 做一次最小 knee 校准。","如果该 family 与 r282 持平或更差，则说明“同一路由对内的 ordered cascade”信息增量不足，后续应转向真正带条件触发语义的 cleanup 结构，而不是继续补 flat-vs-cascade 邻域。","如果本轮出现 sanity 或 dispatch 异常，应把它当 family 集成问题处理，并用同一 exact architecture string 复查训练配置落盘。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮未新增代码；当前工作区已包含 `shared_cascade_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的注册与实现，因此建议以 `param_only` 方式直接首跑该 family。","已在当前工作区重做 exact-string smoke：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_cascade_product_key_expert_jumprelu, K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","已本地校验 override allowlist：对该 family 的 `ARCHITECTURE/K/EXPANSION_FACTOR/OPTIMIZER/LR/AUXK_ALPHA/NUM_EXPERTS/ACTIVE_EXPERTS/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT/STAGE1_RATIO` 调用 `validate_env_overrides(...)` 返回 `[]`。","已本地复核成本：selection_accesses=265216，deployment_accesses=163840，combined_accesses=429056，exact `total_cost_ratio=0.102294921875`；要打赢 r282 objective=0.2684179902076721，需要 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.1661230683326721`。","选择这条线而不是继续回到 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，是因为后者已在 r276 给出 archive objective=0.284106 的负信号，而 shared-cascade 仍是建立在当前 winning scaffold 上、尚未得到首个训练证据的更高信息增量 probe。"],"reference_round":282,"self_review":"这轮满足单变量原则：相对 r282 的完整配置只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。不返回 `edit_sae_code` 是因为本轮没有新增落盘修改，`touched_files=[]` 是有意为之。该提案紧贴当前策略模式“优先压 exceed”，并且比继续扫 `K/NUM_EXPERTS/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 更符合“在 winning scaffold 上测试 genuinely new cleanup semantics”的要求。主要风险是 cascade 会不会因为强制第二个 expert服务残差而损失 flat top-2 的自由度；但这正是当前最值得用一轮 matched-cost architecture probe 回答的问题。","summary":"建议下一轮以 r282 为 patch anchor，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_cascade_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。这是一个直接兼容、同成本附近、尚未首跑的 scaffold-level cleanup 语义升级，目标是专门压低当前 low-K 区间的 `exceed_alpha_0.50`。","touched_files":[]}

